('The Shawshank Redemption', '2', 'Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, \nupstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank \nprison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral \nwarden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired \nby the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his\nintegrity and unquenchable sense of hope. ', 'the shawshnk.jpg', 'Frank Darabont', 'Thomas Newman', 'Niki Marvin', 'Tim Robbins,Morgan Freeman', '1994-02-02', NULL, NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-shawshank-redemption'),
('The Godfather', '2', 'The story spans the years from 1945 to 1955 and chronicles the fictional\nItalian-American Corleone crime family. When organized crime family \npatriarch Vito Corleone barely survives an attempt on his life, his \nyoungest son, Michael, steps in to take care of the would-be killers, \nlaunching a campaign of bloody revenge ', 'godfather.jpg', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Albert S. Ruddy', 'Marlon Brando, AI Pacino', '1999-02-19', 'Excellent movie..Must Watch\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sY1S34973zA', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-godfather'),
