('X-Men: Days of Future Past', '2', 'The X-Men send Wolverine to the past in a desperate effort to change \nhistory and prevent an event that results in doom for both humans and \nmutants ', 'X-Men_Days_of_Future_Past_poster_a852d4710bbc478c82051e471d9b4dcf.jpg', 'Bryan Singer', 'John Ottman', 'Lauren Shuler Donner', 'Patrick Stewart, Hugh Jackman, James McAvoy, Michael Fassbender, Jennifer Lawrence', '2014-05-23', '\n\n\n\n<span itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">This\nfilm is far more sophisticated and has a better story than any X-Men \nmovie to date. The \nmusic is very good as is the special effects.</span> ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pK2zYHWDZKo', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'x-men:-days-of-future-past'),
('Think Like a Man Too', '2', 'All the couples are back for a wedding in Las Vegas, but plans for a \nromantic weekend go awry when their various misadventures get them into \nsome compromising situations that threaten to derail the big event.', 'Screen Shot 2014-06-11 at 12.12.38 pm.png', 'Tim Story', 'Christopher Lennertz', 'Will Packer', 'Michael Ealy, Jerry Ferrara, Meagan Good, Regina Hall', '2014-06-20', NULL, NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'think-like-a-man-too'),
('Transformers: Age of Extinction', '2', 'Autobots must escape sight from a bounty hunter who takes control of the human serendipity: Unexpectedly, Optimus Prime and his remaining gang turn to a mechanic and his daughter for help. ', 'Screen Shot 2014-06-20 at 10.52.03 am.png', 'Michael Bay', 'Steve Jablonsky', 'Don Murphy, Tom DeSanto', 'Mark Wahlberg, Stanley Tucci', '2014-06-27', '\nTransformers: Age of Extinction is a film that wins due to its fantabulous visual and sound effects. While it is a tad-bit too long, no oneâ€™s really complaining, â€™cause there is a lot you can look forward to. From apocalypse, to dinosaurs (now dinobots), to man-made autobots, to family drama, thereâ€™s something in it for everyone. This is the perfect weekend outing for everyone. Explosions and destruction galore, the film is a visual treat in signature Michael ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'transformers:-age-of-extinction'),
('What If (The F Word)', '2', 'It is a romantic comedy based on a play Toothpaste and Cigars. Wallace (Daniel Radcliffe) has a miserable job and lives with his sister and nephew in Toronto. He dropped out of medical school and becomes unsocial after becoming aware of his girlfriend having an affair with his teacher. Things change when he accompanies his friend to a party and meets his cousin while playing a game.', 'The_F_Word_theatrical_poster_opt (1).jpg', 'Michael Dowse', 'Michael Dowse', 'David Gross, Macdara Kelleher, Andre Rouleau, Jesse Shapira, Jeff Arkuss', 'Daniel Radcliffe, Zoe Kazan, Megan Park, Adam Driver, Mackenzie Davis, Rafe Spall', '2014-10-17', 'Watch it for the perfectly simple story, the cinematography, the music and the feeling of love. Itâ€™s also a great change to see Daniel Radcliffe slowly moving away from all the fame he amassed while playing the boy-wizard, Harry Potter, into more serious, mature roles. If youâ€™ve been a fan of the films penned by Nora Ephron, then consider this a tribute of sorts. ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'what-if-(the-f-word)'),
('Kill The Messenger', '2', 'Kill The Messenger is a thriller based on the book with the same name by Nick Schou and the book Dark Alliance by Gary Webb. ', 'Kill_the_Messenger_poster.jpg', 'Michael Cuesta', 'Michael Cuesta', 'Jeremy Renner, Naomi Despres, Pamela Abdy, Scott Stuber', 'Jeremy Renner, Ray Liotta, Barry Pepper, Michael Sheen, Andy Garcia, Mary Elizabeth Winstead, Rosemarie DeWitt, Paz Vega, Oliver Platt, Richard Schiff, Michael K. Williams', '2014-10-17', 'If you are a fan of Jeremy Renner, donâ€™t miss the film. He gives a fine performance as the staunch journalist, Gary Webb. â€‹Kill the Messenger is a vital story in the history of modern journalism and media ethics, that mustnâ€™t be missed.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'kill-the-messenger'),
('Annabelle', '2', 'Annabelle is the prequel of the popular horror film ''The Conjuring''. It begins from the first scene of The Conjuring and moves ahead with the story of John and Mia Gordon who are expecting their first child. John gives her a doll that she apparently has been trying to find. Mia loves it and puts it with the rest of her doll collection in their baby''s room. A murder in the neighbourhood brings their whole world upside down and they look ways to get rid of the doll but they can''t. ', 'annabelle-movie-wallpaper.jpg', 'John R. Leonetti', 'Unknown', 'Peter Safran, James Wan', 'Annabelle Wallis, Ward Horton, Alfre Woodard', '2014-10-10', '\n&nbsp;But, like The Conjuring, the reason Annabelle is more effective than your average horror film is because the acting is pretty solid. It helps that director John R Leonetti (cinematographer of The Conjuring) uses special effects sparingly, choosing instead to craft simple scenes that are steeped in menacing silence. Annabelle isnâ€™t perfect â€“ hell, it isnâ€™t even as good as The Conjuring â€“ but despite its unconvincing climax, itâ€™s got moments of spine-tingling horror that do the tri ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFyZgPpth0E', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'annabelle'),
('Sex Tape', '2', 'When Jay and Annie first got together, their romantic connection was intense â€“ but ten years and two kids later, the flame of their love needs a spark. To kick things up a notch, they decide â€“ why not? â€“ to make a video of themselves trying out every position in The Joy of Sex in one marathon three-hour session.', 'Sex_Tape_(film).jpg', 'Jake Kasdan', 'Not known', 'Steve Tisch', 'Jason Segel,Cameron Diaz', '2014-10-17', 'Disappointing movie ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'sex-tape'),
('Dracula Untold', '2', '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Agreed Dracula is a creature of the night, having forged', 'dracula.jpg', 'Gary Shore', 'Ramin Djawadi', 'Gary Shore', 'Dominic Cooper,Luke Evans', '2014-10-17', 'Acc. to the title, this story aims to tell all is untold about the 15th century Transylvanian tyrant who had the nasty , habit of skewering their heads on tall stakes. Of course in this film, there are many creative liberties thrown in, not all of them savoury. That aside, this is essentially Evans''s vehicle. His version of Dracula is action-oriented rather than horrifying and creepy. And keeping that in mind, he manages, in most parts, to get his teeth into the substance of Count Dracula''s lege', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'dracula-untold'),
('The Judge', '2', 'The Judge is the story of Henry "Hank" Palmer, a successful lawyer who returns to his hometown of Carlinville, Indiana, for his mother''s funeral. But he discovers that his estranged father, Judge Joseph Palmer, is suspected of murder. He is now required to defend his father in court against Dwight Dickham, a prosecutor determined to see Joseph put away.', 'theju.jpg', 'David Dobkin', 'unknown', 'Susan Downey, David Gambino, David Dobkin', 'Robert Downey, Jr., Robert Duvall, Vera Farmiga, Vincent D''Onofrio, Jeremy Strong, Dax Shepard, Billy Bob Thornton', '2014-10-17', '&nbsp;The Judge is a great example of meticulously-crafted character portrayals and a film that carefully builds up each of the main characters over the course of its duration., Hank might be the only one with the chops to defend his dad in a court of law, especially when the prosecution''s seasoned lawyer Dwight (Thornton) is hell-bent on winning. Concurrently, he also rediscovers his roots and even reconnects with a feisty old flame of his. This is a tale encapsulated simply enough within the d', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-judge'),
('Left Behind', '2', 'Left Behind is the story about how millions of people around the globe simply vanish based on a Biblical event called the Rapture which happens without a warning? The story evolves with Lord Jesus collecting his repentant believers and pouring out judgement on the unbelieving and unrepentant.', 'leftbb.jpg', 'Vic Armstrong', 'Unknown', 'Michael Walker, Paul LaLonde', 'Cassi Thomson, Chad Michael Murray, Nicky Whelan, Jordin Sparks, Lance E. Nichols, Martin Klebba, William Ragsdale, Lea Thompson', '2014-10-10', 'The basic premise of the film could have made for an engaging and far-out watch. The very concept of the Rapture could have been depicted with power and mystery, but instead the opposite is achieved in a film that just looks slapdash ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'left-behind'),
('Two Night Stand', '2', 'Two Night Stand is about a pair of twenty-something strangers who wake up after an ill-advised one night stand to find themselves snowed in by a blizzard that''s put all of New York on ice. Trapped together in a tiny Brooklyn apartment, they''re forced to get to know each other far better than any anonymous bed partners should.', '43430545_opt.jpg', 'Max Nichols', 'Unknown', 'Beau Flynn, Ruben Fleischer, Sam Englebardt', 'Raghubir Yadav, Puru Chibber, Reecha Sinha, Rashee, Zakir Hussain', '2014-09-26', 'Two Night Stand has the vibe of a reality show and the feel of a play, where most of the action takes place in Alec''s cozy apartment, in two or three rooms. Teller and Tipton both put in some charming performances. Their delightful repartee is quite clearly the movie''s strongest aspect. It keeps you engaged and is often amusing. While the plot is simple enough, this is, in essence, a pretty candid and contemporary take on young love, with its many colourful details.colourful details. ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'two-night-stand'),
('The Amazing Spider-Man 2', '2', 'When atrocities threaten New York, Spider-Man must protect both its citizens and his loved ones before the city befalls into tragedy.', 'amas.jpg', 'Marc Webb', 'Unknown', 'Alex Kurtzman', 'Andrew Garfield, Emma Stone, Jamie Foxx ', '2014-05-23', 'Peter Parker finds a clue that might help him understand why his parents disappeared when he was young. His path puts him on a collision course with his father''s former partner, Dr. Curt Connors/The Lizard. ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-amazing-spider-man-2'),
('Stonehearst Asylum', '2', 'The movie centers on the experiences of an Oxford Medical School graduate (Jim Sturgess) who becomes obsessed with a mental patient named Eliza Graves (Kate Beckinsale) while working at a mental asylum that''s been taken over by the inmates. ', 'stonehearst-asylum-20141015104119-13909.jpg', 'Brad Anderson', 'Unknown', 'Brad Anderson', 'Kate Beckinsale, Jim Sturgess, Michael Caine, Ben Kingsley, David Thewlis and Brendan Gleeson. ', '2014-10-24', 'With Stonehearst Asylum, director Brad Anderson doles out a vintage Halloween treat â€” a straightforward Poe adaptation of the sort that Vincent Price used to star in â€” and gives it a freshness and complexity that make it a delight.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'stonehearst-asylum'),
('Fury', '2', 'The film is set during the last month of the European Theater of war during World War II in April 1945. As the Allies make their final push into Nazi Germany, a battle-hardened U.S. Army sergeant in the 2nd Armored Division named Wardaddy commands an M4A3E8 Sherman tank called "Fury" and its five-man crew on a deadly mission behind enemy lines. ', 'fury-20141013150440-13907.jpg', 'David Ayer', 'Unknown', 'David Ayer', 'Brad Pitt, Shia LaBeouf, Logan Lerman, Jon Bernthal, Michael PeÃ±a, Jason Isaacs, and Scott Eastwood.', '2014-10-27', 'Watchable movie.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'fury'),
('Serena', '2', 'In Depression-era North Carolina, George Pemberton struggles to maintain the future of his timber empire. His life becomes more complicated when he learns his wife, Serena, cannot bear children. ', 'serena-20140912172133-13848.jpg', 'Susanne Bier', 'Unknown', 'Susanne Bier', 'Jennifer Lawrence and Bradley Cooper as newlyweds Serena and George Pemberton.', '2014-10-30', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'serena'),
('Gone Girl', '2', 'On the occasion of his fifth wedding anniversary, Nick Dunne reports that his wife, Amy, has gone missing. Under pressure from the police and a growing media frenzy, Nick`s portrait of a blissful union begins to crumble. Soon his lies, deceits and strange behavior have everyone asking the same dark question: Did Nick Dunne kill his wife? ', 'Gone_Girl_Poster.jpg', 'David Fincher', 'Unknown', 'David Fincher', 'Ben Affleck, Rosamund Pike, Neil Patrick Harris, Tyler Perry Read more: http://in.bookmyshow.com/movies/gone-girl/ET00022415#ixzz3GUNNsMJv', '2014-10-23', '\nGone girl is one of the best film of the year so far. It is complex, it is creepy, it is satirical, it is some of Fincher''s best work.<br>The cinematography is beautiful, the performances are perfection ( Especially Rosamund Pike ). Â \n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'gone-girl'),
('Horns', '2', 'In the aftermath of his girlfriend''s mysterious death, a young man awakens to strange horns sprouting from his temples. ', 'horns.jpg', 'Alexandre Aja', 'Unknown', 'Alexandre Aja', 'Juno Temple,Daniel Radcliffe', '2014-10-31', '\nBased on the novel by Joe Hill, Horns follows Ig Perrish (Daniel Radcliffe), the number one suspect for the violent rape and murder of his girlfriend, Merrin (Juno Temple). Hungover from a night of hard drinking, Ig awakens one morning to find horns starting to grow from his own head and soon realizes their power drives people to confess their sins and give in to their most selfish and unspeakable impulses ....................................<br>', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'horns'),
('Nightcrawler', '2', '"Nightcrawler" is a pulse-pounding thriller set in the nocturnal underbelly of contemporary Los Angeles. Lou Bloom, a driven young man desperate for work who discovers the high-speed world of L.A. crime journalism.', 'Nightcrawlerfilm.jpg', 'Dan Gilroy ', 'Unknown', 'Dan Gilroy ', 'Rene Russo,Jake Gyllenhaal', '2014-11-07', '\n\nMade with a modest budget, the film highlights the devious tricks of contemporary crime journalism. It lets fear engulf your mind with its threatening silence, dangerous chase sequences, creepy nights and a creepier protagonis. Other than being noirish, Nightcrawler also works as a social satire. It mocks the voyeurism and lack of ethics that the media often shamelessly exhibits. The cinematography is another asset. First-time director ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u1uP_8VJkDQ', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'nightcrawler'),
('The Theory of Everything', '2', 'The Theory of Everything is the story of the most brilliant and celebrated physicist of our time, Stephen Hawking, and Jane Wilde the arts student he fell in love with whilst studying at Cambridge in the 1960s.Little was expected from Stephen Hawking, a bright but shiftless student of cosmology, given just two years to live following the diagnosis of a fatal illness at 21 years of age. He became galvanized, however, by the love of fellow Cambridge student, Jane Wilde, and he went on to be calle', 'the_theory_ee.jpg', 'James Marsh', 'Unknown', 'James Marsh', 'Eddie Redmayne,Felicity Jones', '2014-11-07', 'Visually imaginative, The Theory of Everything is an unusually compelling true-life story about an extraordinary couple triumphing over adversity.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-theory-of-everything'),
('Interstellar', '2', 'The film chronicles the adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage ', 'Interstellar_film_poster_5d49a9c8faf9c603acb03d5439b5686f.jpg', 'Christopher-nolan', 'Unknown', 'Emma Thomas, Christopher Nolan, Lynda Obst', 'Matthew McConaughey,Anne Hathaway,Jessica Chastain,Matt Damon,Casey Affleck,Michael Caine', '2014-11-07', '\n\nStorytelling is a manipulative art form, and by relentlessly plying plot upon plot and event upon event, Nolan slows Interstellar down -- even as the narrative itself attains hyperspeed. And this feeling of an immeasurably long film -- of thinking back in the third act to an opening scene and feeling like it happened many hours ago, many episodes ago, many seasons ago -- is what gives Interstellar its epic breadth.\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zSWdZVtXT7E', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'interstellar'),
('Ouija', '2', 'Ouija uses a fresh concept, which hasnâ€™t been seen a lot in the horror film genre. Unless you count the much better 1986 film, Witchboard. It packs a few scares and has a notable twist that makes it mildly interesting. But beyond that, it just falls apart ', 'ouija.jpg', 'Stiles White', 'Unknown', 'Juliet Snowden, Stiles White', 'Olivia Cooke, Daren Kagasoff, Douglas Smith, Bianca A. Santos, Ana Coto ', '2014-10-31', 'Director Stiles plays it very safe with the jump scares and there is plenty of telegraphing. This only serves to dilute the impact of scenes that would otherwise have given you some serious scares. The spirits also seem to have a fondness for turning on gas stoves. Unfortunately, there are also bits of accidental humor that you would never want to find in a horror film. That said, Cooke does prove herself capable with her role and she does keep the movie from plodding to a standstill. For a movi', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'ouija'),
('Big Hero 6', '2', 'A gorgeously epic film filled with humor, family, fun and robots!', 'BIG_HERO.jpg', 'Don Hall, Chris Williams', 'Unknown', 'Don Hall, Chris Williams', 'Ryan Potter, Scott Adsit, T. J. Miller, Jamie Chung, Maya Rudolph, James Cromwell, Damon Wayans Jr.', '2014-11-07', 'Big Hero 6 attempts to breathe cinematic life into a group of lesser-known Marvel characters, and most definitely succeeds in doing so. Big Hero 6 also provides many moments of genuine sweetness. Furthermore, as apart from other superhero fare, the most powerful weapons in the arsenal are that of kindness, compassion and - as is the case with Baymax - healing. Definitely a delightful film with its heart in the right place. ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bT8qmoCgxZg', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'big-hero-6'),
('John Wick', '2', 'An ex-hitman comes out of retirement to track down the gangsters that took everything from him.<br> ', 'John_Wick_TeaserPoster.jpg', 'David Leitch, Chad Stahelski', 'Unknown', 'Derek Kolstad', 'Keanu Reeves, Michael Nyqvist, Alfie Allen', '2014-11-14', '\nA lean, spare, stylish and grimly, methodically ultra-violent extravaganza that provides star Keanu Reeves with a much-needed infusion of cool. And hard-core action fans with combat-centric cinematic expertise on a par with 20llâ€™s â€œThe Raid.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'john-wick'),
('The Hunger Games: Mockingjay â€“ Part 1', '2', 'After Katniss Everdeen shattered the games forever, Katniss must fight against all odds and save a nation moved by her courage. ', 'MockingjayPart1Poster3.jpg', 'Francis Lawrence', 'Unknown', 'Francis Lawrence', 'Jennifer Lawrence, Josh Hutcherson, Liam ', '2014-11-28', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">The film is a buildup. Colours in D13 as opposed to in the colourful Capitol are deliberately drab and performances, restrained. This is meant to highlight the contrast between the two zones. While it is not as fast-paced as its predecessors, this is however, essential for fans of the series.</span></font>\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-hunger-games:-mockingjay-â€“-part-1'),
('Jessabelle', '2', 'Returning to her childhood home in Louisiana to recuperate from a \nhorrific car accident, Jessabelle comes face to face with a \nlong-tormented spirit that has been seeking her return -- and has no \nintention of letting her escape. ', 'Jessabelle_film_poster.jpg', 'Kevin Greutert', 'Anton Sanko', 'Jason Blum, Jessica L. Hall, Jerry P. Jacobs, Matthew Kaplan, Robyn Marshall, Peter Principato, Paul Young', 'Sarah Snook, Mark Webber, Joelle Carter, David Andrews, Amber Stevens, Ana De La Reguera, Larisa Oleynik, Chris Ellis, Brian Hallisay, Jason Davis, Barbara Weetman, Lucius Baston, Taran Hall, Elizabeth Rowin, Millie Wannamaker', '2014-11-21', 'Surprisingly uneventful, stumbling to an unsatisfying ending that teases complexity and twists, but mostly triggers unenthused shrugs.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'jessabelle'),
('Penguins of Madagascar', '2', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Are the Penguins cute? Of course they are! They are adorable. Does this work as a film? Well, not really! What one would want is a simple story for kids but this one has a lot going on! The adventures don''t stop and just complicate the plot. The penguins are cute, animation and 3D is great! And the running time is just 92 minutes but since the film doesn''t touch the right cord it doesn''t seem worth the time.</span></font>', 'penguins.jpg', 'Eric Darnell, Simon J. Smith', 'Unknown', 'Eric Darnell, Simon J. Smith', 'Tom McGrath, Chris Miller, Christopher Knights', '2014-11-28', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">The film is a buildup. Colours in D13 as opposed to in the colourful Capitol are deliberately drab and performances, restrained. This is meant to highlight the contrast between the two zones. While it is not as fast-paced as its predecessors, this is however, essential for fans of tFour penguins break into Fort Knox for what they consider to be worth more than gold - a vending machine of ''Cheezy Puffs''. Once inside, they are kidnapped by', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'penguins-of-madagascar'),
('Horrible Bosses 2', '2', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Horrible Bosses 2 has a stronger script and funnier gags than the first film. There is never a dull moment. Horrible Bosses 2 is a good enough option if you are over 18 and looking for something to help you and your gang of friends unwind. The film is no masterpiece (and thankfully, it does not pretend that it is) but if dirty jokes tickle your funny bone, Horrible Bosses 2 isn''t so horrible.</span></font> ', 'Horrible.jpg', 'Sean Anders', 'Unknown', 'Sean Anders', 'Jason Bateman, Jason Sudeikis, Charlie Day', '2014-11-28', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Three friends come up with an invention that they hope will make them rich. Soon after they pitch their idea to a business tycoon, they find themselves hoodwinked. They attempt a kidnapping in order to rescue their business. The jokes in the film are largely hit-or-miss. The humour is definitely of the polarising (racial jokes, etc.) variety - you''ll either find it highly amusing or in bad taste. Aniston seems like an unlikely choice for', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'horrible-bosses-2'),
('Exodus: Gods and Kings', '2', 'The defiant leader Moses rises up against the Egyptian Pharaoh Ramses, setting 600,000 slaves on a monumental journey of escape from Egypt and its terrifying cycle of deadly plagues.', 'exodus.jpg', 'Ridley Scott', 'Unknown', 'Unknown', 'Christian Bale, Joel Edgerton, Ben Kingsley', '2014-12-05', 'Whatâ€™s remarkable about Scottâ€™s genuinely imposing Old Testament psychodrama is the degree to which he succeeds in conjuring a mighty and momentous spectacle â€” one that, for sheer astonishment, rivals any of the lavish visions of ancient times the director has given us â€” while turning his own skepticism into a potent source of moral and dramatic conflict.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'exodus:-gods-and-kings'),
('This Is Where I Leave You', '2', 'When their father passes away, four grown siblings are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof together for a week, along with their over-sharing mother and an assortment of spouses, exes and might-have-beens', 'This_Is_Where_I_Leave_You_poster.jpg', 'Shawn Levy', 'Unknown', 'Shawn Levy', 'Jason Bateman, Tina Fey, Jane Fonda ', '2014-12-05', NULL, NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'this-is-where-i-leave-you'),
('The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies', '2', 'Bilbo and Company are forced to engage in a war against an array of \ncombatants and keep the terrifying Smaug from acquiring a kingdom of \ntreasure and obliterating all of Middle-Earth ', 'The_Hobbit_-_The_Battle_of_the_Five_Armies.jpg', 'Peter Jackson', 'Unknown', 'Peter Jackson', 'Ian McKellen, Martin Freeman, Richard Armitage ', '2014-12-12', 'Suitably grim, epic, and action-packed, The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies ends Peter Jackson''s second Middle-earth trilogy on a rousing high note.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-hobbit:-the-battle-of-the-five-armies'),
('Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb', '2', 'Larry spans the globe, uniting favorite and new characters while \nembarking on an epic quest to save the magic before it is gone forever. ', 'Night_at_the_Museum_Secret_of_the_Tomb_poster.jpg', 'Shawn Levy', 'Unknown', 'Shawn Levy', 'Ben Stiller, Robin Williams, Owen Wilson ', '2014-12-25', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'night-at-the-museum:-secret-of-the-tomb'),
('Annie', '2', 'Annie is a young, happy foster kid who''s also tough enough to make her \nway on the streets of New York in 2014. Originally left by her parents \nas a baby with the promise that they''d be back for her someday, it''s \nbeen a hard knock life ever since with her mean foster mom Miss \nHannigan. But everything''s about to change when the hard-nosed tycoon \nand New York mayoral candidate Will Stacks makes a thinly-veiled \ncampaign move and takes her in. ', 'fd_anniegwp_620x350_mlp_v1_lg_cb13ceaf7ab72800069bca3c9789dacf.jpg', 'Will Gluck', 'Unknown', 'Will Gluck', 'QuvenzhanÃ© Wallis, Cameron Diaz, Jamie Foxx |', '2015-01-02', '\nAnnie is light on its feet, frothy, and always insistently, at times provocatively kind, determined to melt grumpy hearts like marshmallows.\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O-lw0Jtmzn8', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'annie'),
('Taken 3', '2', '<p itemprop="description" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0.75em; line-height: 18.2000007629395px; padding: 0px 12px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Ex-government', 'TAKEN3.jpg', 'Olivier Megaton', 'Unknown', 'Luc Besson, Robert Mark Kamen', 'Liam Neeson, Forest Whitaker, Maggie Grace', '2015-01-09', '&nbsp;What works greatly to the movie''s credit is the pacing (never a dull moment here!) and that sense of ''What''s going to happen next?'' Mills and his group of friends rely heavily on technology to stay ahead of the cops as well as to nab the bad guys. Dotzler and team try to predict what Mills will do next. Spruell''s don Malankov, suitably debauched and with a Spetsnaz background, is as nasty and cold-hearted as they come. But Grace''s Kim is really the most riveting. All in all, a suitable swa', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'taken-3'),
('Big Eyes', '2', 'A drama about the awakening of the painter Margaret Keane, her phenomenal success in the 1950s, and the subsequent legal difficulties she had with her husband, who claimed credit for her works in the 1960s.', 'MV5BMjA2ODM5MDE3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTIxNjc1MzE@._V1_SX214_AL_.jpg', 'Tim Burton', 'Unknown', 'Tim Burton', 'Amy Adams, Christoph Waltz, Krysten Ritter', '2015-01-09', '&nbsp;Big Eyes gets you right in the soul. It is a remarkable story that shocked the whole world, and not just the world of art. You are shown a world before instant fame. It talks about the price of being famous. In the end, it shows us that good art is honest and true to the soul of the artist. Tim Burton makes us believe in the Big Eyes. ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xD9uTlh5hI', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'big-eyes'),
('The Woman in Black 2: Angel of Death', '2', '40 years after the first haunting at Eel Marsh House, a group of children evacuated from WWII London arrive, awakening the house''s darkest inhabitant.', 'woman.jpg', 'Tom Harper', 'Unknown', 'Tom Harper', 'Helen McCrory, Jeremy Irvine, Phoebe Fox ', '2015-01-09', 'The stylishness and eerie visual sophistication creates an often unsettling, almost surreal vibe that emphasizes how disconnected they all are from the rest of the world. And the very grin-and-bear-it style Brit stiff upper lip that they try to maintain (Eve and Jean even have time for a spot of tea in the kitchen as they try to figure out what''s going on) adds to the sense of surrealism. Overall, the movie doesn''t rewrite the book of shock (despite the jump scares), but what you get is a fast-p', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-woman-in-black-2:-angel-of-death'),
('Blackhat', '2', 'A furloughed convict and his American and Chinese partners hunt a high-level cybercrime network from Chicago to Los Angeles to Hong Kong to Jakarta ', 'Blackhat_poster.jpg', 'Michael Mann', 'Unknown', 'Michael Mann', 'Chris Hemsworth, Viola Davis, Wei Tang', '2015-01-16', 'Blackhat plays a surprisingly flat and ever-flatter cinema texture against the careful roll-out of an elaborate plot.&nbsp;\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'blackhat'),
('Foxcatcher', '2', 'The greatest Olympic Wrestling Champion brother team joins Team Foxcatcher led by multimillionaire sponsor John E. du Pont as they train for the 1988 games in Seoul - a union that leads to unlikely circumstances. ', 'Foxcatcher_First_Teaser_Poster.jpg', 'Bennett Miller', 'Unknown', 'Bennett Miller', 'Steve Carell, Channing Tatum, Mark Ruffalo', '2015-01-30', '\nFoxcatcher is brilliantly acted and extremely well crafted in a wintry, slow burning way but has an emptiness at its core.Â \n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'foxcatcher'),
('Seventh Son', '2', 'Young Thomas is apprenticed to the local Spook to learn to fight evil spirits. His first great challenge comes when the powerful Mother Malkin escapes her confinement while the Spook is away. ', 'Seventh_Son_Poster.jpg', 'Sergey Bodrov ', 'Unknown', 'Sergey Bodrov ', 'Ben Barnes, Julianne Moore, Jeff Bridges', '2015-01-30', '&nbsp;The sets look like budget Lord of the Rings and the script isn''t really much to write home about. Almost no backstory is offered for any of the main characters or how they connect and it''s also unclear whether the movie is set in medieval Europe or some fantasy world.To be fair, it''s apparent that the most effort has gone into the visual effects and the battles, which are the two redeeming factors about this film.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'seventh-son'),
('Mortdecai', '2', 'Juggling angry Russians, the British Mi5, and an international terrorist, debonair art dealer and part time rogue Charlie Mortdecai races to recover a stolen painting rumored to contain a code that leads to lost Nazi gold.', 'Mortdecai_poster.jpg', 'David Koepp', 'Unknown', 'David Koepp', 'Johnny Depp, Gwyneth Paltrow, Ewan McGregor', '2015-01-23', 'Mortdecai isn''t all that funny, quick-witted, or even that interesting. It''s yet another misunderstood outsider, fish-out-of-water, unreal, and oblivious hero scenario for Johnny Depp.&nbsp; ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mortdecai'),
('BirdMan', '2', 'A washed up actor, who once played an iconic superhero, battles his ego and attempts to recover his family, his career and himself in the days leading up to the opening of a Broadway play. ', 'Birdman_poster.jpg', 'Alejandro GonzÃ¡lez IÃ±Ã¡rritu', 'Alejandro GonzÃ¡lez IÃ±Ã¡rritu', 'Alejandro GonzÃ¡lez IÃ±Ã¡rritu', 'Michael Keaton, Zach Galifianakis, Edward Norton', '2015-01-30', '&nbsp;It''s a riveting portrayal of a fading superhero star who is used as a prop to understand the workings of prestige, power games and how fame''s intoxication can soon wear out into futility and redundancy. Michael Keaton brings palpability to this tailor-made role, in which he seems to mirror his prior experience of playing Batman in two successful stints, only to bow out of it over artistic principles.Birdman, in its 122 minutes'' runtime, transforms into exhilarating cinema that gives a head', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, NULL, 'birdman'),
('Mr. Turner', '2', 'An exploration of the last quarter century of the great, if eccentric, British painter J.M.W. Turner''s life. ', 'Mr_Turner_poster.jpg', 'Mike Leigh', 'Unknown', 'Mike Leigh', 'Timothy Spall, Paul Jesson, Dorothy Atkinson ', '2015-02-06', '&nbsp;Turner was known for his use of light and yet, his own life had plenty of melancholic shades. A depressed soul, however, he was not. He slurs to a young woman at a posh dinner party one evening in between mouthfuls of custard and port, "loneliness and solitude are different." Turner finally does find love and companionship with the widowed landlady, Mrs Booth (Bailey), of a place he often rented. He lives with her, but does not get married. Apart from the fantastic characterizations and to', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mr.-turner'),
('Wild Card', '2', 'When a Las Vegas bodyguard with lethal skills and a gambling problem gets in trouble with the mob, he has one last play...and it''s all or nothing. ', 'Wild_Card_MoviePoster.jpg', 'Simon West', 'Unknown', 'Simon West', 'Jason Statham, Michael Angarano, Dominik GarcÃ­a-Lorido ', '2015-02-06', 'Wild Card doesn''t really do [Statham] any favours, despite its rock-solid supporting cast and storied pedigree.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'wild-card'),
('Kingsman: The Secret Service', '2', 'A veteran secret agent takes a young upstart under his wing. ', 'Kingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg', 'Matthew Vaughn', 'Unknown', 'Unknown', 'Colin Firth, Michael Caine, Taron Egerton ', '2015-02-13', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'kingsman:-the-secret-service'),
('Fifty Shades of Grey', '2', 'Literature student Anastasia Steele''s life changes forever when she meets handsome, yet tormented, billionaire Christian Grey. ', 'FSOG-teaser.jpg', 'Sam Taylor-Johnson', 'Unknown', 'Kelly Marcel', 'Dakota Johnson, Jamie Dornan, Luke Grimes ', '2015-02-13', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'fifty-shades-of-grey'),
('Whiplash', '2', 'A promising young drummer enrolls at a cut-throat music conservatory where his dreams of greatness are mentored by an instructor who will stop at nothing to realize a student''s potential. ', 'Whiplash_poster.jpg', 'Damien Chazelle', 'Unknown', 'Damien Chazelle', 'Miles Teller, J.K. Simmons, Melissa Benoist', '2015-02-20', '\n\nSome might feel that the depiction of jazz here is too harsh. But then again, Fletcher''s approach is about mastering the underpinning forms and structures before a player explores improvisational methods. The taut editing (Tom Cross) is outstanding and Simmons outdoes himself. When the thumping tom-toms, trombones and tympani fall silent, what you are also left with is a career-topping performance (thus far, at least!) from Miles Teller.&nbsp;\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7d_jQycdQGo', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'whiplash'),
('The Gunman', '2', 'A former Special Forces soldier and military contractor suffering from PTSD tries to reconnect with his long time love, but first must go on the run from London to Barcelona and across Europe in order to clear his name. ', 'The_Gunman_poster.jpg', 'Pierre Morel', 'Unknown', 'Pierre Morel', 'Idris Elba, Sean Penn, Javier Bardem ', '2015-02-20', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-gunman'),
('The Lazarus Effect', '2', 'A group of scientists working at a university have discovered a serum that can possibly bring the dead back to life. When a horrible freak accident kills one of them, they make the decision to bring her back. That was a mistake. ', 'TheLazarus.jpg', 'David Gelb', 'Unknown', 'David Gelb', 'Olivia Wilde, Mark Duplass, Evan Peters', '2015-02-27', '\nThe Lazarus Effect may be, itâ€™s a well-crafted and effective horror film that puts you on edge with its creepy premise and does its best to rise above familiar territory. ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-lazarus-effect'),
('Run All Night', '2', 'Mobster and hit man Jimmy Conlon has one night to figure out where his loyalties lie: with his estranged son, Mike, whose life is in danger, or his longtime best friend, mob boss Shawn Maguire, who wants Mike to pay for the death of his own son.', 'runall_.jpg', 'Jaume Collet-Serra', 'Unknown', 'Jaume Collet-Serra', 'Liam Neeson, Ed Harris, Joel Kinnaman ', '2015-03-27', 'We''ve seen Neeson play a tough-as-nails retired cop/hitman/special forces person who rescues various members of his family/public, who also finds his own redemption in the process, for a while now. But somehow, he manages to rock this role every single time, giving action heroes half his age a run for their money. It''s like he''s perfected it down to an art. Albeit an ageing ass-kicker, the Irishman clearly still has what it takes. ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'run-all-night'),
('The Gunman', '2', 'A sniper on a mercenary assassination team, kills the minister of mines of the Congo. Terrier''s successful kill shot forces him into hiding. Returning to the Congo years later, he becomes the target of a hit squad himself.', 'The_Gunman_Official_Theatrical_Poster.jpg', 'Pierre Morel', 'Unknown', 'Pierre Morel', 'Sean Penn, Idris Elba, Jasmine Trinca ', '2015-03-27', 'At one point, an exhausted Jim gasps to Cox, "I don''t want to do this shit anymore!" Wise words, as Penn is best when playing characters with far greater (Mystic River, Dead Man Walking, Milk, I Am Sam, 21 Grams etc) depth, instead. Morel also directed 2008''s Liam Neeson hit Taken. So, whether by conscious design or not, some parallels are inevitable. Idris Elba gets only a cameo, where he has a sort of coded chat with Jim about building treehouses.On the plus side, the fight scenes are unsparin', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-gunman'),
('Dragon Blade', '2', 'Lost Roman soldiers navigate their way through China', 'Dragon_Blade.jpg', 'Daniel Lee', 'Unknown', 'Daniel Lee', 'Adrien Brody, John Cusack, Jackie Chan ', '2015-03-27', '&nbsp;Jackie Chan''s Dragon Blade is a pleasant surprise, executed with visible grandeur and can claim to be an earnestly performed, crisply edited, smart fare. The movie primarily invests in attaining technical finesse to remain close to the widely understood connotation of commercial cinema. Forgoing the attempt to explore the frictional intricacies of Silk Route, the film''s slim understanding of its setting shows starkly in its tendency to avoid a political comment. But, what works in its favo', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'dragon-blade'),
('Get Hard', '2', 'When millionaire James King is nailed for fraud and bound for San \nQuentin, he turns to Darnell Lewis to prep him to go behind bars.', 'Get_Hard_film_poster.png', 'Etan Cohen', 'Unknown', 'Unknown', 'Will Ferrell, Kevin Hart, Alison Brie', '2015-03-27', 'The movie seeks to make you laugh while also risking offense by going too far. It succeeds on both counts.&nbsp; ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'get-hard'),
