('Tamanchey', '6', 'Tamanchey fires off when boy, Munna, a rustic kidnapper from Uttar Pradesh meets girl, Babu, a street smart drug peddler from Delhi. As criminals go, they meet in police custody while being escorted to jail ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Tamanchey1.jpg', 'Navneet Behal', 'Krsna , R.D.Burman, Ikka, Intense, D', 'Suryaveer Singh Bhullar', 'Nikhil Dwivedi,Richa Chadda', '2014-10-10', '\n\n\n\nTamanchey is easily an avoidable film. A movie that celebrates slang like it is the most enriching language ever to narrate a predictable, lame and unconvincing story, there canâ€™t be any kind words for it. <i></i> ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'tamanchey'),
