('Happy New Year', '6', '''Happy New Year'' is the ultimate underdog story where a team of ''losers'', win the love of millions in their quest to pull off the biggest diamond heist ever!! ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/happy_new_year.jpg', 'Farah Khan', 'Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani', 'Shah Rukh Khan, Gauri Khan', 'Shah Rukh Khan,Deepika Padukone,Abhishek Bachchan,Sonu Sood,Boman Irani,Vivaan Shah,Jackie Shroff, Anurag Kashyap, Vishal Dadlani, Dino Morea,Kareena Kapoor Khan,Atishri Sarkar', '2014-10-24', '\nHappy New Year is two distinct films rolled in one. While the first hour is breezy, fun and pretty watchable, the second hour is a convoluted mess with a heist angle that doesnâ€™t work, a romantic track that seems forced, the vivaciousness lacking from the camaraderie of the characters and the sappyness of a dukhbhari daastan of a backstory. It is a half baked film that uses all the regular formulaic heist tools and naturally offers nothing unseen or unexpected. <b', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'happy-new-year'),
('Ekkees Toppon Ki Salaami', '6', 'Two sons set out to get their father what he dreamt of all through his life â€“the ultimate sign of respect. High on thrill and laughter, this film takes the audience through the unbelievable attempt of Shekhar and Subhash Joshi to provide their ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/ekeestpoos.jpg', 'Ravindra Gautam', 'Ram Sampath', 'Abhinav Shukla, Anurradha Prasad Shukla,Jayantilal Gada', 'Anupam Kher,Neha Dhupia,Divyendu Sharma,Manu Rishi Chadha,Aditi Sharma,Rajesh Sharma,Uttara Baokar,Supriya Kumari,Bhagwan Tiwari,Sudhir Pandey,Aasif Sheikh,Anurag Arora,Indresh Malik', '2014-10-10', '\nEkkees Toppon Ki Salaami is not brilliant but somehow it wasnâ€™t too bad either. It is semi watchable and despite its preachy tone, it survives your attention for being essentially noble at heart. I went with far too low expectations and hence probably came out to be a pleasant surprise. If youâ€™re a movie buff who watches every film, this one wouldnâ€™t be too much of a time waste.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'ekkees-toppon-ki-salaami'),
('Mumbai 125 KM', '6', 'On their way to Mumbai from Pune, a bunch of youngsters get stranded on a supposed deserted road that leads to nowhere. Their ill-fated night gets worse as they start witnessing supernatural killings. Can they survive? ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/125km.jpg', 'Hemant Madhukar', 'Mani Sharma, Jsl Singh', 'Hemant Madhukar, Mani Sharma', 'Veena Malik, Vijay Bhatia, Karanveer Bhora, Vedita Pratap Singh, Aparna Bajpai, Joe Debroy, Deana Uppal', '2014-10-17', 'If horror, ghosts and eerie nocturnal elements like bats and graveyards are your thing, catch this movie at your nearest cinema. This movie gives a new spin to an age-old formula. Since it is in 3D, you can truly experience the visual horror.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mumbai-125-km'),
('Super Nani', '6', 'Super Nani is the story of Bharti Bhatia (Rekha) whose every waking hour is devoted to looking after the smallest need and praying for the betterment of her family comprising of her ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/supernani.jpg', 'Indra Kumar', 'Harshit Saxena, Sanjeev Darshan', 'Indra Kumar,Ashok Thakeria', 'Rekha, Sharman Joshi, Shweta Kumar, Randhir Kapoor, Anupam Kher, Rajesh Kumar, Shreya Narayan, Varsha Usgaonkar, Anchal Dwivedi, Vishakha Subhedar', '2014-10-31', '&nbsp;SUPER NANI not only marks the return of Rekha, but also the return of director Indra Kumar to his family drama genre after films like DIL, BETA, etcâ€¦ With SUPER NANI, he has tried to visit the eras of the late eighties and nineties where morals, values, family and traditions were the key words. Since the film is in the hands of such an experienced director, it doesn''t lose its momentum, except for the song and dance sequences, which could have been shot in tune with today''s time and age.', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'super-nani'),
('Mumbai Can Dance Saala', '6', 'Mumbai Can Dance Saala is an upcoming 6 film directed by Sachindra Sharma and produced by Ranjeet Sharma.the film features Ashima Sharma,Prashant Narayanan,Aditya Pancholi,Shakti Kapoor in the lead roles. <br> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Mumbai_can.jpg', 'Sachindra Sharma', 'Bappi Lahiri', 'Ranjeet Sharma', 'Ashima Sharma, Prashant Narayanan, Aditya Pancholi, Shakti Kapoor , Rakhi Sawant, Kiran Janjani, Pankaj Berry, Pradeep Agarwal,Manoj Maru,Rahul Sood,Mukesh Tiwari', '2014-10-31', 'One time watchable movie\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mumbai-can-dance-saala'),
('Roar', '6', 'Uday, a young photojournalist on assignment in the jungles of the Sundarbans, rescues a white tiger cub ensnared in a poacher''s trap and brings the cub to a small settlement he is based in. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/roar.jpg', 'Kamal Sadanah', 'Ramona Arena', 'Abis Rizvi', 'Abhinav Shukla,Himarsha V,Achint Kaur,Subrat Dutta,Virendra Singh Ghuman,Nora Fatehi,Ali Quli,Aaran Chaudhary,Aadil Chahal,Pranay Dixit,Pulkit Jawahar', '2014-10-31', '\nThere are places which make the film look boring and monotonous, but the film''s photography and camera work overshadow the flaws in his direction. The film tends to drag its way with a dull first half, however, the second half is comparatively interesting and engaging, especially towards the end of the film. The film falters mainly because of its poor screenplay and average dialogues. On the whole, despite its decent VFX work, ROAR: TIGERS OF THE SUNDARBANS is a wea', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'roar');
INSERT INTO `Sheet1` (`A`, `B`, `C`, `D`, `E`, `F`, `G`, `H`, `I`, `J`, `K`, `L`, `M`, `N`, `O`) VALUES
('Bang Bang!', '6', 'A chance encounter of the unassuming bank receptionist Harleen Sahni (Katrina Kaif) with the charming yet mysterious Rajveer Nanda (Hrithik Roshan), results in an on-rush of ditched planes ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/bang_20cd94e806e87def2a18b409eac7b', 'Siddharth Anand', 'Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani', 'Fox Star Studios', 'Hrithik Roshan,Katrina Kaif,Danny Denzongpa, Jimmy Sheirgill,Pawan Malhotra,Jaaved Jaaferi', '2014-10-02', '\n\n\nGorgeous stunts, picturesque locales and a paper thin script might create a watchable film but it wonâ€™t be a brilliant or memorable watch.\n\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MGXQ8bE6lW4', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bang-bang!'),
('Fireflies', '6', 'The film is a drama capturing the lives of two estranged brothers. One brother who leads a very successful life as a banker and the other who is a law school dropout and lives by the day. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/89449561.jpg', 'Sabal Singh Sheikhawat', 'Zubin Balaporia ', 'Rakesh Dubey , Sabal Singh Shekhawat , Alan McAlex , Ajay Rai , Shanta Rana , Rajesh Thanickan', 'Rahul Khanna, Monica Dogra, Arjun Mathur, Shivani Ghai, Aadya Bedi', '2014-10-31', 'You can see the movie for its music and singing, or for its perfect performances. Whichever way you look at it, you will not come out disappointed but doubly delighted.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'fireflies'),
('Happy Ending', '6', 'Happy Ending is based on the story of a girl''s journey. It''s an experimental and edgy 90-minute film situated in a four-day time span. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/happy-ending-20141009170325-2889.j', 'Krishna DK,Raj Nidimoru', 'Sachin-Jigar', 'Saif Ali Khan, Dinesh Vijan, Sunil A Lulla', 'Saif Ali Khan,Ileana Dcruz,Govinda, Ranvir Shorey, Kalki Koechlin, Andrew Kneebone,Preity Zinta,Kareena Kapoor Khan', '2014-11-21', '&nbsp;Mostly, Happy Ending''s a fun film with a melodious, modern take on individuals and pyaar. It''s an NRI movie that side-steps dilemmas and pain. And it''s probably the first 6 film where the heroine cheekily tells the hero, "Show your boobs!", performed with polished elan. Wrapping Hollywood ribbons on a Bollywood heart, this is a nice ending - and a good start.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'happy-ending'),
('The Shaukeens', '6', 'Three friends in their 60s try to do everything that they couldn''t do in their younger days before death arrives.Â  ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/The_Shaukeens_2.jpg', 'Abhishek Sharma', 'Yo Yo Honey Singh, Hard Kaur, Vikram', 'Murad Khetani, Ashwin Varde', 'Akshay Kumar,Lisa Haydon,Anupam Kher,Piyush Mishra,Annu Kapoor', '2014-11-07', 'The good thing is that the film showcases exactly what it promises in the promo --- an adult comedy. There are some genuinely funny moments. So if you donâ€™t mind three aged men with high libido and low underwear blatantly hitting on a girl who is oblivious to good touch bad touch (Lagta hain madam ne Satyamev Jayate nahi dekha!), then The Shaukeens might work for you. Watch it only if you are a die-hard Akshay Kumar fan.\n\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'the-shaukeens'),
('Ungli', '6', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;Ungli has a few attributes that you will not usually encounter in a Karan Johar production. It has no big stars, no elaborate song and dance set pieces and no major love story. But when a film is more interesting for what it isn''t than for what it is, giving it a miss might be the most prudent option.</span></font>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Ungli-6-Movie.jpg', 'Rensil Dsilva', 'Salim Merchant, Sulaiman Merchant, S', 'Karan Johar, Hiroo Yash Johar', 'Sanjay Dutt,Emraan Hashmi,Kangna Ranaut,Angad Bedi,Randeep Hooda,Neil Bhoopalam,Neha Dhupia,Shraddha Kapoor, Shiv Subramaniyam', '2014-11-28', '\n<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Rensil D''Silva''s plot is fast-paced, in spite of the many potholes it slips into. He strings the story like episodes, never allowing the drama to intensify. The outlaws have a motive, but their plans are way too improbable and flaky. The film points a finger at our society, and rightly so. But much of the film is pointless too. This work of Rensil''s won''t leave a lasting fingerprint</span></font>\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'ungli'),
('Kill Dil', '6', 'Once upon a time in North India, two killers Dev and Tutu roamed free. Abandoned when young and vulnerable, Bhaiyaji gave them shelter and nurtured them to kill. All is normal in their lives until destiny throws free spirited Disha into the mix. What follows is a game of defiance, deception and love. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/First look poster of Kill Dil.jpg', 'Shaad Ali', 'Shankar Mahadevan, Ehsaan Noorani, L', 'Aditya Chopra', 'Ranveer Singh,Ali Zafar,Parineeti Chopra,Govinda, Sukhwinder Singh, Rocky Verma', '2014-11-14', 'Shaad Ali''s Kill Dil is inspired by countless Hollywood movies that \nshowcase the protagonists romancing the gun. There is enough pizzazz to \ndivert you from the cliched plot. It is certainly a step up from Shaad''s\nlast disastrous outing, Jhoom Barabar Jhoom (2007). And what makes this\nfilm watchable is the effortless chemistry between Ranveer and Ali\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'kill-dil'),
('Rang Rasiya / Colors of Passion', '6', 'More than a century ago, a painter dared to defy the convention and was condemned for doing so. Ketan Mehta''s film ''Rang Rasiya'' tells the story of Raja Ravi Verma and his muse Sugandha. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Rangrasiya.jpg', 'Ketan Mehta', 'Sandesh Shandilya', 'Anand Mahendroo,Deepa Sahi', 'Randeep Hooda,Nandana Sen, Paresh Rawal, Aashish Vidyarthi, Sachin Khedekar, Darshan Jariwala,Jim Boeven, Prashant Narayanan, Rajat Kapoor, Vikram Gokhale, Suhasini Mulay, Tom Alter, Vipin Sharma, Chirag Vohra,Rashaana Shah, G', '2014-11-07', '\nRang Rasiya is more courageous than bold, more sensitive in its narrative than preachy or aggressive and more relevant than any one of his recent films. The canvas and vision of the film is massive and the movie doesnâ€™t step on wrong foot ever, staying brutally honest to what it attempts to say. This is one Ketanâ€™s most effortless, most nuanced and most impactful works and definitely one of recent timesâ€™ most powerful and moving films, I had the good fortune o', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'rang-rasiya-/-colors-of-passion'),
('PK', '6', 'A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, P.K.''s innocent questions and childlike curiosity will take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting-go. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/PK_Theatrical_Poster1.jpg', 'Rajkumar Hirani', 'Ajay-Atul, Ram Sampath', 'Rajkumar Hirani, Vidhu Vinod Chopra', 'Aamir Khan, Anushka Sharma, Sushant Singh Rajput, Sanjay Dutt, Rohitash Gaud, Boman Irani', '2014-12-19', 'Aamir Khan''s PK is a solid entertainer that will surely entertain the masses and classes alike. An outstanding film. Go for it.\n\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'pk'),
('2 States', '6', 'Love marriages around the world are simple. Boy loves girl. Girl loves boy. They get married. In India, there are few more steps... ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/meet-the-2-states-family-new-poste', 'Abhishek Varman', 'Shankar Mahadevan, Ehsaan Noorani, L', 'Sajid Nadiadwala,Karan Johar', 'Arjun Kapoor,Alia Bhatt,Ronit Roy,Amrita Singh,Shiv Subramaniyam,Revathi,Achint Kaur,Aru Krishansh Verma,Madhu Chandok,Nikita Hingorani,Ashwin Kaushal,Bikramjeet Kanwarpal,Mansi Multani,Neeru Chopra,Yashwant Singh,Sanjay Bhati', '2014-04-18', '\n\n\n\n\n\n\n2 STATES is based on Chetan Bhagat''s bestseller ''2 States: The Story Of My Marriage'' Director Abhishek Varman stays faithful to Chetan Bhagat''s bestseller, adapting it delightfully on the big screen. The diverse cultures, the discomfort and the pressures when people talk of inter-caste liaison, the unyielding love and the resolve to win the parents'' trust... each and every aspe ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CGyAaR2aWcA', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, '2-states'),
('Action Jackson', '6', 'Action Jackson is an upcoming Indian action comedy film directed by Prabhudeva and produced by Gordhan Tanwani and Sunil Lulla. The film features Ajay Devgan in the title role, alongside Sonakshi Sinha, Yami Gautam and Manasvi Mamgai as the female leads and Anand Raj, portraying the main antagonist.<br><br> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/actionjakson.jpg', 'Prabhu Dheva', 'Himesh Reshammiya', 'Gordhan Tanwani, Sunil A Lulla', 'Ajay Devgn, Sonakshi Sinha, Yaami Gautam, Manasvi Mamgai, Kunaal Roy Kapur, Rocky Verma', '2014-12-05', 'Action Jackson matches up to neither Prabhudhevaâ€™s film making nor an Ajay Devgn film. It is an extreme downer for those expecting a full on action-packed â€˜masalaâ€™ film. With a done to death plot and an absolutely nothing new to offer, the only thing that this film latches onto is Ajay Devgn who maintains his swagger well enough. I am going with a 1.5/5 for Action Jackson.\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YubQzbzGHps', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'action-jackson'),
('Titoo MBA', '6', 'Titoo (Takhat Singh Gill) is an ambitious Chandigarh boy who dreams of becoming a big businessman. However fate doesn''t favor Titoo and he faces heavy losses in business. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/titoo.jpg', 'Amit Vats', 'Arjuna Harjai', 'Rajan Batra,Mayank Patel', 'Nishant Dahiya,Pragya Jaiswal, Abhishek Kumar', '2014-11-21', '\nTitoo MBA is a light-hearted comedy film with a brief emotional roller coaster ride.\n\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'titoo-mba'),
('Zid', '6', 'Karanvir plays the lead role of Rohan and Mannara as Maya in the movie. Shraddha Das is also played a role in the movie. Rohan is a crime reporter who gets a chance to stay with a girl called Maya in an outhouse, when working on an assignment. They both fall in love with each other. Maya decides to be&nbsp; share her feelings about Rohan to him, while he is not that serious about her at that time. Hearing this and seeing Rohan with another girl, she gets shattered and decides to leave him ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/zid.jpg', 'Vivek Agnihotri', 'Sharib Sabri, Toshi Sabri', 'Anubhav Sinha', 'Karanvir Sharma, Mannara, Mohan Kapoor', '2014-11-28', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Zid'' is nothing like we have never seen before - it''s a story of how love, lust and obsession can drive someone to crime and insanity. Of course, there are the usual suspects - like a love triangle, a cocky detective, some lame witnesses, and stormy nights. The performances are forgettable and flaws scream out loud. The climax tries to shock, but leaves you shaken and wondering - whose zid was this anyway? As the case comes to a painful ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'zid'),
('Zed Plus', '6', 'Zed Plus is story is set in contemporary India in a small town of Rajasthan. A coalition Government, troubled by corruption and communalism, is on the verge of collapsing due to in fights of the coalition partners. All the ministers are making efforts to save the government. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/zedplus.jpg', 'Dr. Chandraprakash Dwivedi', 'Sukhwinder Singh,Nayab', 'Mukund Purohit,Mandira Kashyap', 'Adil Hussain,Mona Singh,Mukesh Tiwari,Sanjay Mishra,Kulbhushan Kharbanda,Rahul Singh,Shivani Tanksale,K K Raina,Ekavali Khanna,Anil Rastogi', '2014-11-28', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;In time, Aslam gets used to his status and the power goes to his head. He is then persuaded into chasing political ambitions. How he copes with it comprises the rest of the film. The narrative, while apparently authentic is overly long, unfocused and takes too long to get to the point to depict its satirical content. The subject matter could have been interesting but it is mired in tedious, very boring, rural and regional cliches t', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'zed-plus'),
('Sulemani Keeda', '6', 'In this slacker bro-mantic comedy, writing partners Dulal and Mainak dream of shaking up the Bollywood film industry in India with their script "Sulemani Keeda"', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/sulemani.jpg', 'Amit Masurkar', NULL, 'Datta Dave, Chaitanya Hegde,Deepa Tracy,Sailesh Dave,Suresh Mhatre', 'Naveen Kasturia,Mayank Tewari,Aditi Vasudev,Karan Mirchandani,Krishna Bisht,Rukshana Tabassum', '2014-11-28', NULL, NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'sulemani-keeda'),
('Lingaa', '6', 'Linga movie is about how a society gets rid of its age-old superstitions.A village that opposes the dam construction insults the laborers and the laborers in turn curse the villagers. Rajini happens to be son of a construction laborer and villagers seek apology of the laborers. Another Rajini comes in here. He befriends the laborer son Rajini in order to bid an escape from the police and investigates the reason behind the dam mishaps and reveals the same to the village people. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/lingaax.jpg', 'K.S. Ravikumar', 'A R Rahman', 'Rockline Venkatesh', 'Rajinikanth,Sonakshi Sinha,Jagapathi Babu,Anushka Shetty,Dev Gill,Santhanam,Karunakaran,Brahmanandam,Radha Ravi,Vijayakumar,K Vishwanath,Manobala,Illavarasu,Prabhu', '2014-12-12', 'Lingaa has pleasing moments to satisfy the Rajinikanth fan in you but the cineaste in you is not properly taken care of. Unlike KS Ravikumar - Rajinikanth''s previous outings, Lingaa has an unexciting storyline with less elements of thriller, but it does offer an entertaining movie-watching experience in a small-scale.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'lingaa'),
('Tevar', '6', 'The concept of film Tevar is a based on college days. Arjun will be playing a regular college guy from Agra, who is a kabaddi champion. He will be practising kabaddi for playing national wide. Meanwhile, he meets Sonakshi Sinha, who will be in troubles. He helps her and the love blossoms in between them. While Arjun plays a Salman Khan fan in the film, Sonakshi plays an Agra girl.<br><br> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/tevar.jpg', 'Amit Ravindernath Sharma', 'Manish', 'Sanjay Kapoor,Boney Kapoor,Sunil A Lulla,Naresh Aggarwal, Sunil Manchanda', 'Arjun Kapoor,Sonakshi Sinha,Manoj Bajpayee, Shruti Haasan, Rajesh Sharma', '2015-01-09', 'Amit Sharma''s Tevar, a remake of the Telugu hit Okkadu (2003), is over-a-decade-old wine served on a larger canvas.the film should''ve been reduced by a good 20 minutes - it doesn''t run quite as fast as Arjun does on screen. Amit makes a smooth progression from 30-second commercials to a 159-minute-long film. His penchant for colours, the right use of the Taj Mahal (as a monument of love), his finesse in presenting the real locations indicate his adroitness in filmmaking.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'tevar'),
('LUV.....Phir Kabhie', '6', 'Coming soon..<br>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/01-luv-phir-kabhie-s.jpg', 'Ajay Yadav', 'Bubli Haque', 'Ajay Yadav', 'Saurabh Roy, Arijita Roy, Meghna Patel, Narendra Bedi', '2014-12-12', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'luv.....phir-kabhie'),
('Badlapur Boys', '6', 'Film ''Veenila Kabadi'', a Tamil super hit film which was directed by Susindran in 2009 isnow being remade in bollywood and it will be called ''Badlapur Boys''. Bollywood editor A Muthu who has edited more than 50 films like Sadak, Deewana, Balwan, Raja Babu, Judwa, Ziddi, Haseena Maan Jayegi has taken the remake rights of film ''Veenila Kabadi'' and turns producer with this film.Badlapur Boys deals with a plot of social family romantic drama with sports as a backdrop and the lead hero Nishan states ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Badhalpur.jpg', 'Shailesh Verma', 'Sachin Gupta, Sameer Tandon, Raju Sa', 'Shailesh Verma', 'Shashank Udapurkar,Annu Kapoor,Anupam Maanav,Kishori Shahane,Aman Verma,Saranya Mohan', '2014-12-12', 'The casting looks flawed too. None of the actors look or behave like Kabaddi players, competing in a ''state-level'' tournament. While predictability of the plot can be forgiven since most sports-based films are about underdogs emerging victorious, the story must strike a chord with the audience, which doesn''t happen here. Kabaddi deserves a better film\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n-jXkwMCD3M', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'badlapur-boys'),
('Main Aur Mr. Riight', '6', 'Main Aur Mr. Right is the story of a young girl Aliya aka Shehnaz who is in search of her Mr.Right. There are four men she proceeds to meet and seems fairly interested in, yet she is unsure of who among them is the most suitable for her title of "Mr.Right". Barun Sobti is playing the role of Sukhi. Every girl dreams of her Mr.Right, but does someone like that really exist? We all know the answer to that, but Aliya has found a solution. She finds an aspiring actor and trains him to the way she w', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/mainaur right.jpg', 'Adeeb Rais', 'Bappi Lahiri', 'Pooja Gujral, Aseem Rais', 'Varun Khandelwal, Danny Saru, Shenaz Treasuryvala, Barun Sobti, Kavi Shastri, Maia Sethna, Anagha Mane, Neha Gosain', '2014-12-12', 'Without Barun, there is clearly nothing to see in the film and hence recommended only if you are a Sobti fan. If not, Main Aur Mr Riight is definitely not for you. And it should never be featured among rom-com movies.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'main-aur-mr.-riight'),
