('Baby', '6', 'The country is perpetually under threat from terrorist powers and the common man walks unaware of the threats and the attacks that our Government controls and prevents. While the common Indian fights for everyday issues, ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/baby-akshay-kumar-movie.jpg', 'Neeraj Pandey', 'Meet Bros Anjjan', 'Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar, Shital Bhatia', 'Akshay Kumar,Tapsee Pannu,Rana Daggubati,Anupam Kher,Danny Denzongpa,Kay Kay Menon,Madhurima Tuli,Rashid Naz, Sushant Singh', '2015-01-23', '\n\n\n\n\n\nBalancing characters, conspiracies and cities, director Neeraj Pandey admirably keeps Baby rich, yet tight, researched, non-sentimental and steely-eyed. Neeraj''s craft has grown - he''s taken trademark touches from films like Special 26 and A Wednesday, setting them here on a grand scale, with a breath-taking climax. Th', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Yu_2nyOP5o', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'baby'),
('Take It Easy', '6', 'This is a story of almost every family, almost every father & son and almost every child in today''s metro cities ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/91575862.jpg', 'Sunil Prem Vyas', 'Unknown', 'Dharmesh Pandit', 'Vikram Gokhale, Dipannita Sharma, Raj Zutshi, Anang Desai, Joy Sengupta, Sulbha Arya, Vijay Kashyap, Supriya Karnik, Jyoti Gauba, Yash Ghanekar, Prasad Reddy, Smera Jadhav', '2015-01-02', '\nThe movie highlights the current trend of forcing children to be the best at everything, even if it means pushing them to their physical and emotional limit. It highlight the story of one such kid, who has to deal with his demanding parents and also survive all the odds at school.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'take-it-easy'),
('Sharafat Gayi Tel Lene', '6', 'The movie is about Prithvi Khuranna (Zayed Khan), a middle class working professional who walks into an ATM booth and discovers that his bank balance jumped from less than Rs. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/sharafat.jpg', 'Gurmmeet Singh', 'Dhruv Dhalla, Sandeep Chatterjee, Me', 'Devinder Jain, Akhilesh Jain', 'Zayed Khan, Tena Desae, Talia Bentson,Rannvijay Singh, Anupam Kher', '2015-01-16', 'Even though the film''s director Gurmmeet Singh has tried his level best to weave a story spanning the life of a middle class working professional, the essence of the same still seems to be lost in transit. The medium paced first half of the film is followed by the fast moving second half which also provides fodder to many an unearthing. Gurmmeet could have tightened the directorial noose a bit more than the existing (esp. in the climax, when the plot''s secret is revealed). This definitely could ', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'sharafat-gayi-tel-lene'),
('I', '6', 'I, which is basically targeted at the South Indian film industry, will have to depend heavily on the word-of-mouth in order to do good business in 6 film circuit. A very special mention to the make-up (Sean Foot and Davina Lamont) and also to the team which has done the film''s VFX work. On the whole, go for I only if you are a big fan of extravagant masala films.<br>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/i.jpg', 'Shankar', 'A R Rahman', 'V. Ravichandran', 'Chiyaan Vikram,Amy Jackson,Suresh Gopi,Upen Patel,Mohan Kapoor', '2015-01-14', 'This is certainly not Shankarâ€™s best work. The film maker who is usually known for making films with messages and whose heroes are the society changers, this love story with a beauty and the beast twist is quite ordinary. It will be a disappointment for those who are fans of Shankarâ€™s work but a thorough entertainer if you love Vikram. The actor is worth a watch for his brilliant performance. If you have three hours to kill, well you could try this!\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'i'),
('MSG: The Messenger of God', '6', 'The Messenger of God is a revolutionary film with a gripping story-line. The film is packed with all the right elements to make it an entertainer.<br>It tries to prove that spirituality can be full of fun, self-confidence and peace! So say goodbye to drugs and alcohol, and welcome spiritualism! ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/msg.jpg', 'Gurmeet Ram Rahim Singh Ji Insan', 'Gurmeet Ram Rahim Singh Ji Insan', 'Ravi Verma', 'Gurmeet Ram Rahim Singh Ji Insan,Fllora Saini,Daniel Kaleb,Jayshree Soni,Olexandra Semen,Gaurav Gera,Jay Singh Rajpoot', '2015-02-13', 'As a result of poor and amateurish direction, the film tends to suffer big time, and starts looking and behaving as a propaganda documentary of Ram Rahim Singh Ji Insan. If MSG: THE MESSENGER is anything to go by, then, (with his noble intentions notwithstanding), Ram Rahim Singh Ji Insan has miles to go in the department of direction and storytelling. On the whole, MSG: THE MESSENGER is a film that can be watched once... purely for the dynamics and the histrionics of the endearing Gurmeet Ram R', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'msg:-the-messenger-of-god'),
('Rahasya', '6', 'Film is based on the infamous Arushi murder case. The film explores the plight of a couple who have not only lost their only child but who also have to bear the trauma of the father being accused of killing his... ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/rahasya.jpg', 'Manish Gupta', 'Ranjit Barot', 'Monica Vimal Maluka', 'Tisca Chopra,Ashish Vidyarthi,Baby Sakshi Sem,Kay Kay Menon, Meeta Vasisht, Ashwini Kalsekar, Manoj Maurya, Vinit Kakar', '2015-01-30', '\nÂ It''s quite evident that Manish Gupta''s Rahasya is somewhere inspired by the high profile Noida double murder case of Aarushi Talwar and Hemraj. To make the film dramatic and interesting a lot of fictional characters are added for a good who-done-it murder mystery. There are times when your eyes are on the screen to just know what will happens next. If you enjoy murder mysteries then you must watch Rahasya. It''s a well-made film.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'rahasya'),
