('Badlapur', '6', 'Badlapur is all fury and fog, a revenge saga that plays out with great&nbsp; eyebrow-singeing intensity, says Raja Sen. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/a-two-faced-varun-dhawan-on-the-ne', 'Sriram Raghavan', 'Sachin, Jigar', 'Dinesh Vijan, Sunil A Lulla', 'Varun Dhawan,Huma Qureshi,Yaami Gautam,Nawazuddin Siddiqui,Vinay Pathak,Divya Dutta,Radhika Apte, Kumud Mishra, Pratima Kazmi', '2015-02-20', '\n&nbsp;Badlapur is a gobsmacking movie that suffuses on screen - a deftly written story, spectacular performances and an intelligently layered screenplay. What works best here is the film''s unpredictability. From the minute it begins, you''re latched to your seat with your heart throbbing in your mouth and your throat frequently choking up. For the sheer impact the movie conjures up, writer-director Sriram Raghavan deserves a bow\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9KEoZanqlOE', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'badlapur'),
