('Detective Byomkesh Bakshy!', '6', 'In a contemporary interpretation of war torn Calcutta during the 1940''s, the film follows the first adventure of Byomkesh (Sushant Singh Rajput), fresh out of college, ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/detectivex.jpg', 'Dibakar Banerjee', 'Sneha Khanwalkar,Madboy, Mink', 'Aditya Chopra', 'Sushant Singh Rajput,Anand Tiwari,Swastika Mukherjee,Divya Menon,Neeraj Kabi', '2015-04-03', '&nbsp;As far as the film is concerned, even though it''s a whodunit thriller, the thrill of watching a thriller gets lost midway through the film. In the name of a whodunit genre, the film goes overboard totally, thus, resulting into the film falling flat on the face. On the whole, DETECTIVE BYOMKESH BAKSHY! can be skipped, without any regrets.&nbsp;\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'detective-byomkesh-bakshy!'),
('Ek Paheli Leela', '6', 'A story that took 300 years to complete itself...it is believed that the story revolves around re-incarnation and revenge. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/lellax.jpg', 'Bobby Khan', 'Meet Bros Anjjan, Amaal Mallik, Dr. ', 'Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar, Ahmed Khan, Shaira Khan', 'Sunny Leone,Jay Bhanushali,Mohit Alawat,Rajniesh Duggal,Rahul Dev,Jas Arora,Shivani Tanksale', '2015-04-10', '\nThis movie is a voluptuous feast for the eyes, and I am not only referring to the film''s heroine who is supremely confident in her skin. It''s the aura of the film. Stunningly mounted and sumptuously narrated,Ek Paheli Leela is a feast for the senses. Ms Leone''s assets and the sand dunes of Jaisalmer with equal affection.Sunny Leone fills up the screen with her voluptuous presence.The twist in the climax is jolting.Ek Paheli Leela is the surprise of the year.', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'ek-paheli-leela'),
('Mr. X', '6', 'Emran hashmi has invisible power in this movie... he has played a brilliant character as a selfish scientist who has only one thing in his mind- success of the experiment even at the cost of killing endlessly. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Mr.X.jpg', 'Vikram Bhatt', 'Ankit Tiwari, Ankur Tiwari, Jeet Gan', 'Mukesh Bhatt', 'Emraan Hashmi,Amyra Dastur, Nora Fatehi', '2015-04-17', '\n\n<span class="tabdata storynormal" id="toitabdata">Mr. X is watchable and engaging but shows spark in parts. It has a solid \nstory in place, but the sharp twists fail to maintain the consistency of\nthe drama. However, what works in this film is its intention to deliver\nsomething different.</span>\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mr.-x'),
('Jai Ho! Democracy', '6', 'Jai Ho Democracy takes a comic look at the way the powers-that-be love to procrastinate and maintain status quo, unfazed by the gravity of situations at hand. It explores the hilarity of the levels to which the media can go to sensationalize issues. It also gives a message of hope to peace through a glimpse of a utopian possibility, albeit momentary, between the armies of the two neighbouring nations.<br> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/jai hodemo.jpg', 'Ranjit Kapoor', 'Unknown', 'Bikramjeet Bhullar', 'Om Puri,Annu Kapoor,Satish Kaushik,Seema Biswas, Adil Hussain,Aamir Bashir,Grusha Kapoor,Benjamin Gilani ', '2015-04-24', '\n<span class="tabdata storynormal" id="toitabdata"><strong></strong> It \nall starts with an irrelevant incident. After spotting a hen in no man''s\nland, across the LOC between India and Pakistan, a junior cook of the \nIndian army is forced to enter the forbidden land to claim the Murgi. As\nsoon as the youngster is pushed into the area, Pakistani soldiers open \nfire objecting this move. The Indians demand that they should be allowed\nto retaliate.</span>\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'jai-ho!-democracy'),
('Solid Patels', '6', 'Tom Patel and Jerry Patel are no less than real life animated characters and have stepped into a haphazard Mumbai life laced with comic paradox and meandering aimlessness ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Solid-Patels-Poster-.jpg', 'Saurabh Varma', 'Hanif Shaikh', 'Ranjit Thakur, Nitika Thakur', 'Shiv Pandit,Shazahn Padamsee,Vaishali Desai,Varun Badola,Kettan Singh,Manoj Joshi,Kitu Gidwani,Ali Asgar,Snehal Dhabi,Ranjeet', '2015-05-22', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'solid-patels'),
('Margarita With A Straw', '6', '<span class="tabdata storynormal" id="toitabdata"><strong></strong>Laila has a love of life - and cerebral palsy. Tasting bittersweet flavours, does Laila come of age?</span> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/with_a_straw.jpg', 'Shonali Bose', 'Mikey McCleary', 'Shonali Bose', 'Kalki Koechlin,Revathi,Sayani Gupta,Hussain Dalal', '2015-04-17', '\n\n\n<span class="tabdata storynormal" id="toitabdata">So, a Margarita is \nusually sweet - but this one has a cutting edge. Laila (Kalki) loves \nmusic, romance and people - but cerebral palsy impairs her motor \nfunctions. Laila''s loving mother Shubhangi (Revathi) supports her \nthrough college. But what happens when Laila meets Khanum (Sayani) and \ndiscovers new shades to her sexuality?<br> </span>\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'margarita-with-a-straw'),
('Phir Se...', '6', 'A separated couple living in London, trying to come to terms with the consequences of their split. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/phirse.jpg', 'Kunal Kohli, Ajay Bhuyan', 'unknown', 'Shiv Kumar', 'Kunal Kohli, Jennifer Winget', '2015-05-15', '\n\n\n\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'phir-se...'),
('Gabbar Is Back', '6', 'Gabbar Singh Rajput (Akshay Kumar) creates his own vigilante military network called the Anti-Corruption Force (ACF) that eliminates the most corrupt individuals, from all walks of life. As pressure builds on Police and Government to track down the man who masterminds these killings, Balbir Singh (Sonu Sood) is heading the task. He is aided by Suryam (Prakash Raj) who, though being just a constable in the mammoth Police force, is compelled by his instincts to see through the underlying design.&n', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/gabbar.jpg', 'Krish', 'unknown', 'Sanjay Leela Bhansali,Shabina Khan', 'Akshay Kumar, Shruti Haasan, Amala Paul, Prakash Raj, Sonu Sood,Chitrangda Singh,Kareena Kapoor Khan, Sunil Grover, Suman Talwar', '2015-05-01', '\nThe film is a complete entertainer filled with punchlines, action and an absolutely hot Akshay Kumar. Gabbar Is Back is a typical massy commercial film which thrives on its lead star Akshay Kumar. The story is highly predictable but if you are a fan of films that have dialogues like â€˜Sher Ka Shikaar Karna Ho Toh Bakri Ko Aankhon Ke Saamne Rakhna Padta Haiâ€™ then this one is your sure shot weekend watch.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'gabbar-is-back'),
('Mastizaade', '6', '<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);">Two womanizing bachelors fall in love with twin sisters who run a sex addiction clinic.</span> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Masti.jpg', 'Milap Zaveri', 'Unknown', 'Pritish Nandy', 'Sunny Leone,Tusshar Kapoor,Vir Das,Milap Zaveri', '2016-01-29', '\n<div><div><font color="#444444" face="Roboto, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 28px;">&nbsp;Mastizaade is the result of a fractured script. Word in the trade circles is that this so-called adult comedy was reportedly assaulted by the CBFC! So what you see, in the current running time of less than two hours, is a disjointed mishmash of some stupid sex jokes, tacky in-house product placement clips, Sunny Leone''s tasteful skin show and two blundering idiots - Tusshar and Vir. Both actors should have realised that they ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QWa2QQHpVHg', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mastizaade'),
('Piku', '6', 'A quirky take on the father-daughter relationship. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Piku.jpg', 'Shoojit Sircar', 'Unknown', 'Ronnie Lahiri', 'Amitabh Bachchan, Deepika Padukone, Irrfan Khan, Jishu Sengupta, Moushumi Chatterjee,Akshay Oberoi', '2015-05-08', 'Piku''s story is stunning. It beautifully explores the most basic bond of life - a parent, a child, a beginning and an end. It looks shyly at love. It smiles tenderly at Bengali flavours, at fish fry and digestion pills, but also at universal stories, of irritating relatives and domestics who look after us until we die.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'piku'),
('Kuch Kuch Locha Hai', '6', 'The film is about Ram Kapoor, who plays a rich Gujarati businessman and Sunny Leone, who is a famous film star. The situations they find themselves in lead to funny moments. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Kuchkuchlocha.jpg', 'Devang Dholakia', 'Unknown', 'Mukesh Purohit', 'Ram Kapoor, Sunny Leone, Evelyn Sharma, Navdeep Chhabra', '2015-05-08', 'Kuch Kuch Locha Hai has a really tepid start. Touted as a comedy, there is hardly a scene to laugh with or at. All the movie does is play with ridiculous stereotypes we have seen in countless 6 movies â€“ loud Gujaratis, fake foreign accents, effeminate gays and many other stupid things try to make us laugh but fall flat. Sunny Leone has appeared only in a few scenes till now. Instead, we have been subjected to Ram Kapoorâ€™s hammy performance and Navdeep Chhabraâ€™s expressionless face.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'kuch-kuch-locha-hai'),
('Bombay Velvet', '6', 'An ordinary man goes against all odds and forges his destiny to become a ''Big Shot''. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Bombayvelvet.jpg', 'Anurag Kashyap', 'Amit Trivedi', 'Anurag Kashyap,Vikramaditya Motwane,Vikas Bahl,Madhu Mantena', 'Ranbir Kapoor,Anushka Sharma,Manish Choudhary,Kay Kay Menon,Karan Johar, Siddhartha Basu, Remo Fernandes, Satyadeep Mishra, Mukesh Chhabra, Vivaan Shah', '2015-05-15', '&nbsp;Bombay Velvet is like a fake gold jewelry, it shines bright with its look and feel, and performances but inside is a not-so-polished plot that is evident beyond all its pomp and jazz. So if you are a true Anurag Kashyap Fan, you may not like his commercial bend, but overall the film is worth a watch for is grandiose.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bombay-velvet'),
('Barkhaa', '6', 'It is an Intense unconditional sensitive love story between two radically opposite people.', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/62588-thumb.jpg', 'Shadaab Mirza', 'Amjad Nadeem', 'Shabana Hashmi', 'Sara Loren, Taaha Shah, Priyanshu Chatterjee, Shweta Pandit, Puneet Issar', '2015-03-27', '&nbsp;BARKHAA is Shadaab Mirza''s debut film as a director and his script is filled with numerous flaws. With an absolutely vague and directionless script, the film fails to hold your attention. It is far from entertaining. Shadaab fails to establish the connection between the flashback and the present day scenes convincingly. The length of the film is another deterrent. Overall, Shadaab fails to deliver, both, as a director as well as the screenplay writer (along with Lawrence John). On the whol', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N-kD5HNRG4A', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'barkhaa');
INSERT INTO `Sheet1` (`A`, `B`, `C`, `D`, `E`, `F`, `G`, `H`, `I`, `J`, `K`, `L`, `M`, `N`, `O`) VALUES
('Sabki Bajegi Band', '6', 'The film will unveil deep and dark secrets of the glamour world and may turn out to be one of the most controversial films of 2015<span style="float:left;" name="advenueINTEXT" id="advenueINTEXT"><em> </em></span> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/sabkibajegi.jpg', 'Anirudh Chawla', 'Vishal Khurana', 'Yusuf Shaikh', 'Sumeet Vyas, Swara Bhaskar, Alekh Sangal, Shaurya Chauhan, Amol Parasher, Aman Uppal, Jhanvi Desai, Samarth Shandilya, Nisha Lalwani, Raj Kumar Yadav', '2015-05-01', '&nbsp;Despite of many expectations about the movie, to know the inner Bollywood, The movie much portrays mostly on the sex life and personal questions of the characters in the movie. Not watchable with family. Can be seen as a time pass movie.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'sabki-bajegi-band'),
('Tanu Weds Manu Returns', '6', 'Tanu and Manu''s marriage collapses. What happens when Manu meets Tanu''s lookalike Kusum - and when Tanu returns? ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/tanuu.jpg', 'Aanand. L. Rai', 'Surjrdb-Rdb Rythm Dhol Bass', 'Sunil A Lulla, Krishika Lulla', 'R Madhavan,Kangna Ranaut,Dhanush,Jimmy Sheirgill,Eijaz Khan,Swara Bhaskar,Deepak Dobriyal,Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub,Rajendra Gupta,Navni Parihar,K K Raina,Dipti Mishra,Rajesh Sharma', '2015-05-22', '&nbsp;Tanu Weds Manu Returns with double fun - and philosophy. It''s hard to love happily. Yet, so easy. Aanand L. Rai merits applause for his masterful direction of Himanshu Sharma''s rich, riotous story. Evoking a new-age Hrishikesh Mukherjee, Rai keeps things tight, light, yet layered - and handles two leading ladies, one of whom deserves an extra half-star. Sorry, Tanu - but Kusum is truly something else. Like a certain Kangana who''s returned - and how.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'tanu-weds-manu-returns'),
('Welcome 2 Karachi', '6', 'The movie is a one-of-a-kind comedy adventure of how two cool adventurers find themselves in Karachi, Pakistan amidst the political tension and a super sexy surprise element from Pakistan, KK who essays the role of an ISI agent on chase. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/kaarchi.jpg', 'Ashish R Mohan', 'Jeet Ganguly, Rochak Kohli,Amjad Nad', 'Vashu Bhagnani', 'Jackky Bhagnani,Arshad Warsi, Lauren Gottlieb, Imran Hasnee, Adnan Shah', '2015-05-28', 'Difficult to pick out the worse part, the weak content or the awful special effects.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>\n\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'welcome-2-karachi'),
('P Se PM Tak', '6', '&nbsp;Kasturi (Meenakshi Dixit) is the unapologetic prostitute, who wears her heart on her sleeve. A random police raid forces her to leave the brothel and seek refuge in Satara, where she bumps into inspector Rajan (Indrajeet Soni). It''s love at first sight for her but he is committed to a highly influential politician''s (Bharat Jadhav as Waman) niece. Since it''s election time, Rajan puts Kasturi behind bars as instructed by Waman &amp; co. One thing leads to another and in no time Kasturi find', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/PSE_PM.jpg', 'Kundan Shah', 'Jatin', 'Dhaval Jayantilal Gada, Reshmaa Kadakia, Akshay Jayantilal Gada', 'Meenakshi Dixit, Rocky Verma, Bharat Jadhav, Yashpal Sharma, Deepak Shirke, Akhilendra Mishra, Mushtaq Khan, Anand Kale, Vedish, Geetanjali Kulkarni, Virendra Saxena, Upasana Singh, Pandharinath Kamble, Sanjay Dadhich, Anjan S', '2015-05-29', 'How a prostitute bags a prominent post in the constitution is what forms the story. Sadly, the writing and execution is so poor, dated and pointless that you wonder why anyone would make a film like this. To begin with, there is no humour in this supposed comedy. The lead actress tries her best to seem crass and thus sounds like a bhajiwali, kaamwali and a prostitute all rolled into one. Her imitation of a sex worker is anything but realistic.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'p-se-pm-tak'),
('I Love Desi', '6', 'This film is based on the DDLJ where our hero Vedant (Punjab Singh) is in dreams of Simran and the Priyanka (Simran) to make his property marries with Punjab Singh. Later they reach to Punjab Singhâ€™s village were the show exactly startsâ€¦ ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/I_LUV.jpg', 'Pankaj Batra', 'Toshi Sabri, Sharib Sabri, Sham Balk', 'Rocky Daswani', 'Vedant Bali, Priyanka Shah, Gulshan Grover, Shakti Anand, Krip Suri, Mannat, Arun Bali, Sunita Dheer, Baby Tiya, Guggi,Soniya Gill', '2015-05-29', '\nI Love Desi is a forgettable soundtrack and ironically there is no title song in there either. The one that you wish to play on a repeat mode though is ''Dil Ka Baje Ektara''. <br><br>\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'i-love-desi'),
('Dil Dhadakne Do', '6', 'On a cruise to celebrate their parents'' 30th wedding anniversary, a brother and sister deal with the impact of family considerations on their romantic lives. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/dildakaneso.jpg', 'Zoya Akhtar', 'Shankar Mahadevan, Ehsaan Noorani, L', 'Ritesh Sidhwani, Farhan Akhtar', 'Farhan Akhtar,Ranveer Singh,Priyanka Chopra,Anushka Sharma,Anil Kapoor,Shifaali Shah,Ridhima Sud,Rahul Bose, Zarina Wahab, Parmeet Sethi, Vikrant Massey, Manoj Pahwa,Aamir Khan', '2015-06-05', 'Dil Dhadakne Do is not a massy film and that is where it may lose a good chunk of its audience. The film has a distinctive approach towards familial bonds and that may not go well with everyone.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'dil-dhadakne-do'),
('Hamari Adhuri Kahani', '6', 'Vasudha''s (Vidya Balan) husband, Hari (Rajkummar Rao) disappears, leaving her holding their baby alone for almost five years. But she gets a chance at love again when she meets the hotel tycoon, Aarav (Emraan Hashmi) who falls for her hook, line and sinker.&nbsp; ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/humariadhuri.jpg', 'Mohit Suri', 'Jeet Ganguly, Mithoon, Ami Mishra', 'Mukesh Bhatt', 'Emraan Hashmi, Vidya Balan,Rajkummar Rao,Amala,Madhurima Tuli', '2015-06-12', 'What the film could have been, and which it briefly is, is about a woman, who, despite her over-bearing reality, breaks free from tradition, follows her heart and triumphs. Instead, she stupidly walks with her suitcase into the sand dunes. No, this is not an incomplete story. Itâ€™s just a badly told one.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'hamari-adhuri-kahani'),
('Mere Genie Uncle', '6', 'A laugh-riot with a subtle message of love and compassion. To excite kids this X''mas specially prepared a song Christmas Day...', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Genie.jpg', 'Ashish Bhavsar', 'Nyzel Dlima', 'Rajesh Shah, Ashish Bhavsar', 'Tiku Talsania,Swati Kapoor,Anuj Sikri,Shakti Kapoor,Ehsaan Qureshi,Navina Bole,Mushtaq Khan,Ashish Roy,Pankaj Kalra,Pratham Kalra,Yash Acharya,Ayyan Mallik,Jannat Khan,Hetvi Charla', '2015-06-05', NULL, NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'mere-genie-uncle'),
('ABCD - Any Body Can Dance - 2', '6', 'Two guys go to Mumbai to fulfill their dreams. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/55899cfea84d9.image.jpg', 'Remo Dsouza', 'Sachin,Jigar', 'Siddharth Roy Kapur', 'Varun Dhawan,Shraddha Kapoor,Prabhu Dheva,Lauren Gottlieb,Raghav Juyal,Punit Pathak,Dharmesh Yelande,Prachi Shah', '2015-06-19', '\nABCD 2 is a complete entertainer filled with delightful dance performances. Undoubtedly, Indiaâ€™s best attempt at making a wholesome dance film. Every dancer in the crew is pitch perfect and Remo Dâ€™Souza deserves a â€˜This Is Itâ€™. Whatâ€™s Bad: Whilst Remo makes sure there is nothing missing on the dance front, the plot takes a backseat. In terms of story, the screenplay is mediocre. Also the overstretched run time is a downer for a 3D film.\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IKUtAC-dwFM', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'abcd---any-body-can-dance---2'),
('Miss Tanakpur Haazir Ho', '6', 'Miss Tanakpur Haazir Ho is a political satire running along a perilous love-story based in Tanakpur, a village in Haryana. Haryana, where the village''s Pradhans in general have insurmountable powers ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/misstanakpur.jpg', 'Vinod Kapri', 'Palak Muchhal,Sushmit Sen', 'Vinay Tiwari', 'Annu Kapoor,Hrishita Bhatt,Rahul Bagga,Ravi Kissen,Sanjay Mishra,Kamlesh Gill,Bhupesh Pandya,Om Puri', '2015-06-26', '&nbsp;Miss Tanakpur Haazir Ho comes across as a strained attempt at replicating Jolly LLB-esque storytelling.Sanjay Mishra brings some comedic heft to the filmâ€™s handful of funny moments.Like many of its peers, Miss Tanakpur takes off with a great premise but fails to realise its full potential.&nbsp;\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'miss-tanakpur-haazir-ho'),
('Bezubaan Ishq', '6', 'BEZUBAAN ISHQ, a beautiful love triangle &amp; a musical, is spiced with breathtaking cinematography and beautiful lyrical song. It''s the story of Suhani, Swaagat and Rumzum creating a contemporary love triangle with traditional values. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/bezubaan-ishq-first-look-poster_14', 'Jashwant Gangani', 'Babli Haq, Rupesh Verma', 'Jashwant Gangani, C.J.Gadara, Dinesh Likhiya', 'Nishant Malkani,Mugdha Godse, Sneha Ullal,Farida Jalal, Sachin Khedekar,Darshan Jariwala,Smita Jaykar,Muni Jha, Alexandra Ahlmann, Soniya Mehta', '2015-07-03', '\nThe plot, stitched with numerous songs, seems forced and the situations contrived\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPygTLo1Bsg', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bezubaan-ishq'),
('Uvaa', '6', 'Ram, Anil, Vikram, Salmaan and Deenbandhu are the rebellious brats of suburban Delhi NCR, with the world at their feet and nothing to worry they stomp everything in their path without knowing the consequences, but challenge lay ahead when all of them are put in a totally new world of convent school, here they survive and thrive only to find love.But one night they encounter a horrifying event which puts them in the hands of law. Their lives change forever, they have to fight for justice and mor', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/uvaa.jpg', 'Jasbir B. Bhati', 'Rashid Khan, Palash Muchhal, Hanif S', 'Anil D. Jethani,Chandresh D. Jethani', 'Vikrant Rai,Rohan Mehra,Lavin Gothi,Mohit Baghel,Bhupendra Singh,Meghvrat Singh,Vinti Idnani,Sheena Bajaj,Yukti Kapoor,Neha Khan,Jimmy Sheirgill,Archana Puran Singh,Monish Chodhary,Rajit Kapoor,Elena Kazan,Sanjay Mishra,Jeetu ', '2015-06-26', '\nVarious films raise issues and portray aam junta''s plight, their silent \nprotests and outrage against the system, but fail to offer a credible \nsolution to fight the crime. Uvaa dares to do that and manages to make \nsense somewhere, but shoddy execution mars this potentially significant \nsocial drama, which demands crucial changes in our judiciary and society\nat large.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'uvaa'),
('Guddu Rangeela', '6', 'Two cousins GUDDU (Amit Sadh) and RANGEELA (Arshad Warsi) run a small-town orchestra party while moonlighting as informants for local gangs. While younger impetuous Guddu can''t keep his hands off women, Rangeela is still fighting a hopeless court case to avenge the killing of his wife BABLI years back at the hands of local political leader BILLO (Ronit Roy). When a local "PR for the Underworld" ASHFAQ gives them a chance to make quick money to pay off the new corrupt Inspector and to continue t', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/guddu.jpg', 'Subhash Kapoor', 'Amit Trivedi,Subhash Kapoor', 'Sangeeta Ahir', 'Arshad Warsi,Amit Sadh,Aditi Rao Hydari,Ronit Roy,Dibyendu Bhattacharya, Amit Sial, Brijendra Kala, Rajiv Gupta, Sree Swara Dubey', '2015-07-03', 'Yet Guddu Rangeela never quite soars.The ingredients are all there and there are times itâ€™s all good and rollicking, but a lot of it seems slapped hurriedly together. The fact that Guddu and Rangeela are a couple of weary dogsbodies who, according to their theme song, ''drink down their own tears, neat'' is never shown to us, only told. Still, itâ€™s a decent ride.Itâ€™s no Ishqiya, but at least it has some heart.&nbsp;\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'guddu-rangeela'),
('Hum Sab Ullu Hain', '6', 'Hum Sab Ullu Hain is a nonstop comedy film with a whole lot of comedy actors playing the central characters. In a rainy situation, with the roads blocked, a few of the characters get shelter in a bungalow and then starts a roller coaster ride. Confusions, Misunderstandings, Difficulties, Solutions and lot of laughter! ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/hum-sab-ullu-hain_banner1_14400557', 'T Manwani Anand', 'Yug Bhusal, Laxmi Narayana, Dhaval T', 'Sona T Manwani', 'Gavie Chahal,VIP,Rakesh Bedi,Rajesh Puri,Upasana Singh,Guddi Maruti,Vishnu Sharma,Sunil Pal,Sandeep Malani,Surinder Singh,Ayesha,Pranay,Vandana Lalwani,Amruta Chabbria,Rajeev Ngam,Sanjay Wadekar,Sujoita Mukherjee', '2015-09-11', '\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7TGsXNc8VjY', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'hum-sab-ullu-hain'),
('Second Hand Husband', '6', 'Duty manger at a five star hotel, Rajbir (Gippy Grewal) is in love with Gurpreet (Tina Ahuja), a lawyer. The two want to get married but that''s not possible until Rajbir''s divorce with his first wife Neha (Geeta Basra) comes through. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/second.jpg', 'Smeep Kang', 'Badshah, Jatinder Shah, Surinder Rat', 'Iqbal Singh, Palwinder Singh, Manwinder Singh, Gurvinder Singh', 'Dharmendra, Gippy Grewal,Narmada Ahuja, Deepshikha, Geeta Basra, Vijay Raaz, Mukesh Tiwari, Ravi Kishan, Alok Nath, Sanjay Mishra', '2015-07-03', 'Neha asks for hefty alimony. Rajbir finds her demands unreasonable so starts looking for a guy, who could marry her and fulfil her wishes. His groom-hunting forms the story.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'second-hand-husband'),
('I Love NY', '6', 'This is a one-night story - it''s New Year eve and two strangers living in two different cities [New York/Chicago] are tossed into each other''s company by the hand of fate in a comedy of errors that''s as funny as it is enchanting. And just as the world is celebrating New Years, the two stranger''s realise their own romances are falling apart...<br>Making a desperate bid to sustain their own relationships they inadvertently fall in love over one magical New Year''s eve... ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/ILUV_NY.jpg', 'Radhika Rao,Vinay Sapru', 'Pritam Chakraborty, Falak Shabir, R.', 'Kishan Kumar,Bhushan Kumar', 'Sunny Deol, Kangna Ranaut, R Madhavan, Prakash Raj, Manoj Joshi, Tannishtha Chatterjee, Reema Lagoo, Virag Mishra, Surekha Sikri, Navin Chaudhary, Prem Chopra, Farzil Pardiwalla, Lilette Dubey, Maya Alagh', '2015-07-10', '\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'i-love-ny'),
('Thoda Lutf Thoda Ishq', '6', 'Two good for nothing boys Jhumru and Ghumru are best examples of fools who keep roaming around the whole day. Their sole motive in life is to have fun, befriend girls, go to parties, get drunk and chill. They find impish ways to get in touch with girls.They are also desperate to get a job, but in their comical attempt they receive yet more embarrassment. After couple of disasters they get a job at a newly opened beauty parlor run by two smart girls. Their dream has come true. They are around gi', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/THODA.jpg', 'Sachin Gupta 1', 'Vikram Khajuria', 'Bharat Bansal,Vivek Yadav,Sachin Gupta 1', 'Hiten Tejwani,Rajpal Yadav,Sanjay Misra,Neha Pawar,Bhavita Anand,Sushmita Mukherjee,Rakesh Bedi', '2015-07-10', 'What you expect to be a hilarious trip turns out to be just another stodgy comedy with unfunny jokes.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'thoda-lutf-thoda-ishq'),
('Bahubali', '6', 'A dispute between two brothers', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Baahubali.jpg', 'S.S. Rajamouli', 'M.M. Kareem', 'Karan Johar', 'Prabhas,Rana Daggubati,Anushka Shetty,Tamannaah Bhatia,Sathyaraj,Nasser,Ramya Krishnan,Sudeep,Adivi Sesh,Tanikella Bharani,Rakesh Varre', '2015-07-10', 'From the first frame itself, my eyes were glued to the screen as I could see why Baahubali is the most extravagant film of India. From covering wide expanses of waterfalls, forests and mountains to erecting a whole city with a mix of real locations and computer effects, Baahubali takes you on a visual retreat that will linger for days. ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sOEg_YZQsTI', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bahubali'),
('Bin Roye (Pakistani)', '6', 'An ambitious girl seeks out her destiny and true love , when tables start to take a turn she meets a man who gives her a completely new perspective to life and love.<br> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/binroye.jpg', 'Shahzad Kashmiri,Momina Duraid', 'Unknown', 'Momina Duraid', 'Humayun Saeed,Mahira Khan,Armeena Rana Khan, Javed Sheikh, Zeba Bakhtiyar, Azra Mansoor', '2015-07-17', '\nPerfect acting, beautiful faces, breathtaking locations and a gripping story\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bin-roye-(pakistani)'),
('Bajrangi Bhaijaan', '6', 'A young mute girl from Pakistan loses herself in India with no way to head back. A devoted man with a magnanimous spirit undertakes the task to get her back to her motherland and unite her with her family. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/bajrangi.jpg', 'Kabir Khan', 'Pritam Chakraborty', 'Salman Khan, Rockline Venkatesh', 'Salman Khan,Kareena Kapoor Khan,Harshaali Malhotra,Nawazuddin Siddiqui,Deepti Naval,Ali Quli Mirza,Adnan Sami,Najeem Khan, Sharat Saxena, Alka Kaushal,Krunal Pandit', '2015-07-17', '\nÂ Bajrangi Bhaijaan is Salman Khan''s most daring film where Salman presents a beautiful performance - but allows the story to be the real dabangg. Pawan (Salman) aka ''Bajrangi'' is a devout Shri Hanuman bhakt who meets a speech-impaired child (Harshaali) wandering alone, hungry and silent. Bajrangi decides to help the child, whom he calls Munni, return to her family - which is in Pakistan.\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vyX4toD395U', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bajrangi-bhaijaan'),
('Masaan', '6', 'Four lives intersect along the Ganges: a low caste boy in hopeless love, a daughter ridden with guilt of a sexual encounter ending in a tragedy, a hapless father with fading morality, and a spirited child yearning for a family, long to escape the moral constructs of a small-town. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/masaan11.jpg', 'Neeraj Ghaywan', 'Indian Ocean', 'Anurag Kashyap,Vikas Bahl,Vikramaditya Motwane,Manish Mundra,Guneet Monga', 'Vicky Kaushal, Richa Chadda, Sanjay Mishra, Shweta Tripathi', '2015-07-24', '\n&nbsp;The premise of â€˜Masaanâ€™ is fairly engaging. Parallel stories of two young people who have grown up surrounded by the Hindu rites of death, already establish that their circumstances are a disadvantage. How traditional small towns norms can damage a personâ€™s life is subtly argued. The film is effective without filmy drama.\n\n\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'masaan'),
('Bangistan', '6', 'Two blundering terrorists with lofty ideologies, but ordinary talent, on a mission to change the world. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/bangistan_7e0f32470c15249af99fd092', 'Karan Anshuman', 'Ram Sampath', 'Farhan Akhtar,Ritesh Sidhwani', 'Riteish Deshmukh, Pulkit Samrat, Chandan Roy Sanyal, Akash Pandey, Aarya Babbar, Kumud Mishra,Jacqueline Fernandez, Aakash Dabhade, Shiv Subramaniam', '2015-08-07', '\nThe director, who wishes to depict the futility of war fought in the name of God and religion, stays on track. Despite the dry choice of subject, Bangistan makes valiant attempts to keep the humour alive during its two-hour running time.The characters of Riteish and Pulkit, who do not have a single mean bone in their bodies, are convincing as the Dumb and Dumber combo; blundering bumpkins who are a misfit on a terror journey. <br> ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uPtyOoYL12Y', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bangistan'),
('Aisa Yeh Jahaan', '6', 'A young Assamese couple - Rajib (Dr Palash Sen) and Ananya (Ira Dubey) revive their love and seek to rectify their fast-growing detachment from family, their cultural roots and nature.<br> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Aisayeh.jpg', 'Biswajeet Bora', 'Dr. Palash Sen', 'Maya Kholie', 'Dr. Palash Sen', '2015-07-24', '\nAisa Yeh Jahaan is quaint and leaves the audience with several striking questions towards the end. Weaving several issues together, director Biswajeet Bora has spun a fine yarn with the film. It is also Indiaâ€™s first carbon-neutral film- the crew have planted 400 saplings around the country, making up for carbon emission during the production of the film.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6tC7wgEAna0', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'aisa-yeh-jahaan'),
('Drishyam', '6', 'Desperate measures are taken by a man who tries to save his family from the dark side of the law, after they commit an unexpected crime. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Drishyam.jpg', 'Nishikant Kamat', 'Vishal Bhardwaj', 'Kumar Mangat Pathak, Abhishek Pathak, Ajit Andhare', 'Ajay Devgn,Tabu,Shriya Saran,Rajat Kapoor,Ishita Dutta,Mrinal Jadhav', '2015-07-31', 'Regurgitating a tried &amp; tested template of a successful Malayalam film, Drishyam becomes a gripping, layered watch in itâ€™s second half. Tabu is brilliant, &amp; Rajat Kapoor complements her ably with a subtle act.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'drishyam'),
('Calendar Girls', '6', 'The film focuses on five girls who hail from different regions of India, and who have been selected to pose for the country''s most prestigious annual calendar which is a joint effort between business tycoon Rishabh Kukreja and his photographer friend Timmy Sen ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Calendar-Girls_e1b43e3ea8166abcd48', 'Madhur Bhandarkar', 'Meet Bros Anjjan, Amaal Mallik', 'Madhur Bhandarkar, Sangeeta Ahir', 'Akanksha Puri, Avani Modi, Kyra Dutt, Ruhi Singh, Satarupa Pyne', '2015-09-25', '\n\n&nbsp;\nCalendar Girls is only about sex and sleaze presented on the pretext of unravelling the decaying innards of Bollywood and the cricketing world. It talks incessantly and very loudly about spot-fixers, sex racketeers, cheating husbands, corporate loudmouths and builders seeking a toehold in showbiz but never makes any sense at all. <br> ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wg77MZddikg', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'calendar-girls'),
('Jaanisaar', '6', '&nbsp;Love in times of war. Set in pre-independent India, the film captures the love story of a king and a courtesan, in the backdrop of a revolution looming against the British. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Jaanisaar.jpg', 'Muzaffar Ali', 'Muzaffar Ali, Ustad Shafqat Ali Khan', 'Meera Ali', 'Imran Abbas,Pernia Qureshi,Muzaffar Ali,Dalip Tahil,Beena Kak', '2015-08-07', '&nbsp;''Inspired by true events'', Jaanisaar begins with Naseeruddin Shah''s voice over telling us how the British had initially thought it was impossible to capture the then wealthy India because of its rich heritage and culture. If they were to do so, they had to kill this very ''tehzeeb'' which made us invincible.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'jaanisaar'),
('Brothers', '6', 'The film tells the story of a broken family, set in the world of mixed martial arts and underground street fighting. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/bROTHERS.jpg', 'Karan Malhotra', 'Ajay Gogavale, Atul Gogavale', 'Karan Johar, Hiroo Yash Johar', 'Akshay Kumar,Sidharth Malhotra,Jackie Shroff,Jacqueline Fernandez,Ashutosh Rana,Shifaali Shah,Kareena Kapoor Khan', '2015-08-14', 'â€˜Mukkasâ€™ and mush can go together, but not when the latter threatens to \ndrown the former. When the tough get going, audiences are happy to \ntoughen it out too. Here we see the brothers go at each other, limbs \nsnapping at each blow, and all we can hear is â€˜bhaiyyaaaâ€™.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'brothers'),
('Manjhi The Mountain Man', '6', 'True Story of a Man Who Broke A Mountain, for Love. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Manjhi.jpg', 'Ketan Mehta', 'Sandesh Sandilya', 'Ketan Mehta', 'Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Radhika Apte', '2015-08-21', '\n\n&nbsp;What could have been a bland boring representation of a real life story, Manjhi turns out to be just like his signature dialogue- â€œShaandaar Zabardast Zindabadâ€. This inspiring tale is appalling and gladly brilliantly executed. Manjhi is like Indiaâ€™s Thor â€“ the man with the hammer and a determination even stronger than that!&nbsp;\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'manjhi-the-mountain-man'),
('All Is Well', '6', 'This is a story where entire family is on the run, being chased by goons. It''s a dysfunctional family; everyone has their own set of issues with each other - waiting to be confronted. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/all-is-well-poster-4_3a0473596b4ac', 'Umesh Shukla ', 'Himesh Reshammiya, Amaal Mallik, Mit', 'Bhushan Kumar,Krishan Kumar,Varun Bajaj', 'Abhishek Bachchan, Asin, Rishi Kapoor, Supriya Pathak,Sonakshi Sinha, Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub, Harry Josh', '2015-08-21', '\nThis film ends up creating a road trip that keeps going round and round till the viewerâ€™s head is seriously spinning, when suddenly the end is near.The only good thing about the film is it ends in two hours. All is not well with All Is Well.Not a good movie to watch<br> ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wlyc0NxmRYs', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'all-is-well'),
('Ishq Click', '6', NULL, 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Ishq_CLICK.jpg', 'Anil Balani', 'Unknown', 'Ajay Jaiswal,Satish Tripathi', 'Adhyayan Suman, Sara Loren, Keshav Arora, Sanskkriti Jain', '2015-08-21', '\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'ishq-click'),
('Phantom', '6', 'A disgraced Indian soldier carries out a series of assassinations in the hope of restoring his honour. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/pHANTOM.jpg', 'Kabir Khan', 'Unknown', 'Sajid Nadiadwala, Siddharth Roy Kapur', 'Saif Ali Khan,Katrina Kaif', '2015-08-28', 'A big problem with Phantom is that itâ€™s never fast-paced and slick like the Bond or Bourne film that it so badly wants to be. This is Saif playing Rambo essentially, but each time he picks up a gun, you want to say: â€œRakh de yaar, chal jayegi.â€Iâ€™m going with a generous two out of five for Phantom. The jingoistic dialogue and the filmâ€™s questionable message aside, this is boring, inert stuff. The directorâ€™s last film Bajrangi Bhaijaan feels like Citizen Kane in comparison\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'phantom'),
('Kaun Kitney Paani Mein', '6', 'A satire on water set in the rain shadow areas of Orissa where water becomes currency in our daily life. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Kaun-Kitne-Panni-Mein-KKPM.jpg', 'Nila Madhab Panda', 'Krishna Beura, Bishakh-Kanish, Style', 'Nila Madhab Panda,One Drop', 'Kunal Kapoor,Radhika Apte,Gulshan Grover,Saurabh Shukla,Robin Das,Hema Singh,Devender Chaudhary,Ekavali Khanna', '2015-08-28', '\nÂ Water is important, and there are many ways to convey it to a film audience. You can go for a really serious documentary on conservation or you can weave a satirical story around the idea. If youâ€™re interested in a crash course on the latter, hereâ€™s director Nila Madhab Pandaâ€™s 110-minute film Kaun Kitney Paani Mein. To begin with, itâ€™s an intelligently executed film\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'kaun-kitney-paani-mein'),
('Welcome Back', '6', 'The plot of Welcome Back will be much more confusion and promises to offer many more moments of Laughter as it revolves around the love story of Shruti Haasan and John Abraham who are wooed by a underworld don played by Naseeruddin Shah. Nana Patekar and Anil Kapoor will yet again be seen playing the loyal members of Naseeruddin Shahâ€™s team. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Welcome.jpg', 'Anees Bazmee', 'Anu Malik, Meet Bros Anjjan, Yo Yo H', 'Firoz Nadiadwala, Sunil A Lulla', 'John Abraham,Anil Kapoor,Nana Patekar,Shruti Haasan,Paresh Rawal,Supriya Karnik,Dimple Kapadia,Naseeruddin Shah,Adi Irani,Mushtaq Khan,Snehal Dhabi,Ankita Srivastava,Sara Loren, Shiney Ahuja, Harry Josh, Neeraj Vora,Surveen Ch', '2015-09-04', 'Unlike the previous film where Akshay Kumar held everything together. \nJohn Abraham tries his best to do an Akki act, but a weak script pulls \nhim down again and again. Welcome Back is funny in parts, but that \nâ€˜Welcomeâ€™ fluidity is missing big time. There are moments but they are \nvery limited in number. Welcome Backâ€™s pace is its biggest asset and \nthat may make you enjoy this 153-minute long film. \n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'welcome-back'),
('Hero', '6', 'A boy and a girl find themselves stuck in a whirlpool of such intense \nlove that they would do anything, go to any extent and face all odds for\nthe one they love. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Hero.jpg', 'Nikhil Advani', 'Jigar, Amaal Mallik,Meet Bros Anjjan', 'Salman Khan, Subhash Ghai', 'Sooraj Pancholi,Athiya Shetty, Govinda, Vinod Khanna, Sharad Kelkar, Salman Khan,Tigmanshu Dhulia,Aditya Pancholi', '2015-09-11', 'Hero is a complete throwback of the â€˜Ek Gunda Ek IG Ki Beti Se Kaise Pyaar Kar Sakta Haiâ€™ era. Nikhil Advani misses out on presenting a completely entertaining plot. All the elements seem scattered and hence there is neither enough romance nor action nor drama. The screenplay is a little hotchpotch and that is what affects the film badly.\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0B5pRrXWFkI', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'hero'),
