('Puli', '6', 'A young man travels back in time machine to a fantasy kingdom to save its queen from the tyrant commander Sudeep. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Puli.jpg', 'Chimbu Deven', 'Devi Sri Prasad', 'Shibu Thameens, PT Selvakumar', 'Vijay, Sridevi, Sudeep, Shruti Haasan, Hansika Motwani, Vijaykumar, Robo Shankar, Sathyan, Jasper, Imman Annachi, Nandita Shweta, Shivaji Prabhu, Gayatri Raman', '2015-10-01', 'f you are a die-hard Vijay fan then you may but if you are looking for something unique, the film will fail you. It creates an illusion of being smart but in reality, it lacks any kind of logic.\n\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'puli'),
('Singh Is Bliing', '6', 'The whole story is that Amy doesn''t know how to speak 6 and I don''t know how to speak English and our romance has started. But there is a communication gap. She can''t understand me and I can''t get a word of what she says, so we call for a translator and Lara as Emily is the translator. The whole film is about how she messes up my love story. Because if the translator is messing things up, then the whole story is going to go haywire and that''s what this beautiful love story is all about. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Singh-is-Bliing-HD-Wallpapers-Post', 'Prabhu Dheva', 'Sajid, Wajid, Meet Bros Anjjan, Manj', 'Ashvini Yardi', 'Akshay Kumar,Amy Jackson,Lara Dutta,Kay Kay Menon,Prabhu Dheva,Yograj Singh,Rati Agnihotri,Arfi Lamba,Anil Mange,Pradeep Rawat,Sunny Leone, Kareena Kapoor Khan,Kunal Shashi Kapoor, Harry Josh,Murli Sharma', '2015-10-02', '&nbsp;Don''t go expecting logic in the story, as this is a quirky comedy that solely relies on superstar Akshay''s swag to keep you entertained. Amy Jackson is a revelation as she plays her feisty character well and so do the supporting actors. After a hilarious first half, a few inconsequential scenes and random songs follow but Prabhudheva smartly reverses the gender roles of his lead cast, thus adding some novelty to the proceedings\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nuVAGjO-s2I', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'singh-is-bliing'),
('Talvar', '6', 'Nyodda is fictional dramatization of true life events revolving around Aarushi Talwar murder case investigation. The thriller is a work of fiction which is based on one of the most intriguing and talked about double murder case in recent history. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/talwar-first-poster.jpg', 'Meghna Gulzar', 'Vishal Bhardwaj', 'Vineet Jain,Vishal Bhardwaj', 'Irrfan Khan,Avika Gor,Konkona Sen Sharma,Sohum Shah,Tabu,Neeraj Kabi, Atul Kumar, Gajraj Rao', '2015-10-02', '\nStraight away, Talvar is super-sharp, a sword swipe at Bollywood''s song-and-dance, mehendi-fuelled escapism. Inspired by 2008''s Aarushi Talwar double murder case, for which Aarushi''s parents are serving a life-term, Talvar takes reality head on - and turns it on its head.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'talvar'),
('Jazbaa', '6', 'Anuradha Varma (Aishwarya), a reputed criminal lawyer, agrees to defend a convicted felon to save her missing daughter. What follows is a moral and social dilemma between the hardened lawyer and the hapless mother. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/jazbaa-MAIN_3d04567f9b814be440a62b', 'Sanjay Gupta', 'Unknown', 'Sanjay Gupta,Akash Chawla, Nittin Keni, Sachiin Joshi, Raina Sachiin Joshi, Anuradha Gupta', 'Aishwarya Rai Bachchan,Irrfan Khan, Shabana Azmi,Chandan Roy Sanyal, Jackie Shroff, Atul Kulkarni, Abhimanyu Shekhar Singh, Priya Banerjee', '2015-10-09', '\n\nAishwarya goes for the jugular in this crime thriller. Inspired by the South Korean thriller Seven Days, Jazbaa revolves around a divorced lawyer, who dotes on her pre-teen daughter. With a 100 per cent success track record, she knows how to get any criminal ''justice''. However, her world crumbles when her daughter goes missing. The kidnapper makes it clear that he is not interested in money. Rather, he tells her that the only way she will ever see her child again is to free a felon (Chandan) who ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nx7z1enCLWs', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'jazbaa'),
('Pyaar Ka Punchnama 2', '6', 'After falling in love, three roommates experience changes in their lives. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Pyaar ka punchnama2.jpg', 'Luv Ranjan', 'Hitesh Sonik, Sharib Sabri, Toshi Sa', 'Abhishek Pathak', 'Kartik Aaryan,Nushrat Bharucha,Sunny Singh Nijjar,Omkar Kapoor,Sonalli Sehgall,Ishita Sharma 1, Sharat Saxena', '2015-10-16', 'The story or premise is basically the same as Part I. But it is tweaked and garnished with different detailing to make it appear different. If you have really enjoyed Part I, then you wonâ€™t mind this one too but donâ€™t expect a lot of fu\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tC-HGUhxyyc', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'pyaar-ka-punchnama-2'),
('Wedding Pullav', '6', 'The film with the theme of two best friends all set to get hitched...but to two other persons. Confusion starts when their hidden feelings come out. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Wedding-Pullav-Movie-2015indiandha', 'Binod Pradhan', 'Salim Merchant,Sulaiman Merchant', 'Shashi Ranjan', 'Anushka Ranjan, Diganth Manchale, Karan Grover, Sonalli Sehgall, Rishi Kapoor, Satish Kaushik, Parmeet Sethi, Kitu Gidwani, Himani Shivpuri, Upasna Singh, Tripta Lakhanpal', '2015-10-16', '\nThe film''s music (Salim-Sulaiman) is the saving grace and boasts of two hummable songs in the form of ''Party Karni Hai'' and ''Oh Jaaniya''. On the other hand, the film''s background music (Rohit Kulkarni) leaves no impact on the audiences. The film''s cinematography (Gopal Shah) is decent. The film''s editing (Sayyed Sameer) is very clumsy and could have been better by leaps and bounds. The film''s poor script and screenplay, doubled up with sloppy editing lands up making a ''khichdi'' of the dish called ''WEDDING PULLAV''.\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mqhcr4QZE6s', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'wedding-pullav'),
('Bumper Draw', '6', 'Bumper Draw is a hilarious film about two characters - Sunderlal & Farooq who befriend each other in a strange situation. After which, they both encounter Pestonji, an old Parsi man who adds to their existing list of problems. However at the end, Pestonji is the one who turns out to be a reward for both of them. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/bumper.jpg', 'Irshad Khan', 'Rahul Mishra', 'Irshad Khan', 'Rajpal Yadav,Zakir Hussain,Subrat Dutta,Rushad Rana,Bomi Dotiwala,Omkar Das Manikpuri,Seema Azmi,Deepa Sethi,Reena Charnya,Sitaram Panchal,Narendra Bedi,Hrishikesh Joshi,Meera', '2015-10-16', 'The film begins with the same Parsi old man narrating this very story to a young TV reporter. His tale revolves around taxi driver Farooque (Rajpal Yadav), William visa wala (Subrata Datta) and other such troubled characters that get involved with the two for money. Each has a legitimate reason to unintentionally hold the elderly man hostage. Victims of circumstances, their plan keeps going awry until truth about the man surfaces.\n', NULL, '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bumper-draw'),
('Shaandaar', '6', 'A young boy finds his love in a mysterious way. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/shaandaar-movie-trailer-Shahid-Kap', 'Vikas Bahl', 'Amit Trivedi', 'Anurag Kashyap,Madhu Mantena,Vikramaditya Motwane,Karan Johar', 'Shahid Kapoor,Alia Bhatt,Pankaj Kapoor,Sanah Kapoor, Sanjay Kapoor,Sushma Seth,Diljit Dosanjh,Anjana Sukhani,Karan Johar', '2015-10-22', '\nShaandaar is different from his other flicks alright, but itâ€™s far from being brilliant. Bahlâ€™s scenes are seen falling flat most of the time, and he isnâ€™t even able to whip out something to keep us captivated during the boring parts. He however succeeds in bringing out the best from his actors. He and the ever so impressive Anil Mehta deserve credit for capturing some jaw dropping locations as well. The film would have received a lot of help if some of its songs and unneeded sequences were chopped off.\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k99-vMPh3-A', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'shaandaar'),
('Prem Ratan Dhan Payo', '6', 'A king, who is loved by his subjects, wants to lead a normal life away from all the responsibilities and his kingdom, while his step brother plans to steal the throne from him. But things are changed when the king finds out the common man who looks exactly like him and they change their identities with each other temporarily. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Premratan.jpg', 'Sooraj Barjatya', 'Himesh Reshammiya', 'Sooraj Barjatya', 'Salman Khan,Sonam Kapoor, Neil Nitin Mukesh, Armaan Kohli, Anupam Kher, Swara Bhaskar, Deepak Dobriyal, Sanjay Mishra, Sucheta Khanna, Samaira Rao, Rakesh Bedi, Kapil Jhaveri', '2015-11-12', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">&nbsp;If you want to relive the HAHK times, this could be your pick. There is everything you will find in a Rajshri film and hence it will appeal to you only if you are a fan of their films which are all about values, traditions and love for oneâ€™s family Prem Ratan Dhan Payo is not everyoneâ€™s cup of tea! It is a family watch and best for those who love to watch happy endings with emotional undertones. This is a typical Rajshri affair so watch it only if y', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vd4iNPuRlx4', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'prem-ratan-dhan-payo'),
('Main Aur Charles', '6', '<span style="color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 18.2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The movie review&nbsp;</span>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/unnamed-311.jpg', 'Prawaal Raman', 'Aditya Trivedi', 'Raju Chadha, Amit Kapoor, Vikram Khakhar', 'Randeep Hooda, Richa Chadda, Tisca Chopra, Adil Hussain, Mandana Karimi, Lucky Morani, Nandu Madhav, Alexx ONeil, Dijana Dejanovic', '2015-10-30', '\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wOF9MlEOfuE', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'main-aur-charles'),
('31 October', '6', '31st October, the first mainstream film ever based on the assassination of Indira Gandhi and what it led to. Set against the backdrop of 1984 anti-Sikh riots, the film is a true-life story of a Sikh family and their fight for survival. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/31.jpg', 'Shivaji Lotan Patil', 'Unknown', 'Harry Sachdeva', 'Vir Das, Soha Ali Khan, Daya Shanker Pandey, Vineet Sharma, Deepraj Rana, Raj Saluja, Nagesh Bhonsle, Sezal Sharma', '2015-10-26', '\n\n\nOctober 31st says about the Indian politics and the up''s and down''s which are effecting the present India''s scenario, It will showcase the struggle and community relationship.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CucGte4wKzI', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, '31-october'),
('Titli', '6', 'In the badlands of Delhi''s dystopic underbelly, Titli, the youngest member of a violent car-jacking brotherhood plots a desperate bid to escape the ''family'' business. ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/titli.jpg', 'Kanu Behl', 'Unknown', 'Dibakar Banerjee', 'Shashank Arora,Ranvir Shorey,Amit Sial,Shivani Raghuvanshi,Lalit Behl', '2015-10-30', '\n\n<span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">In the badlands of Delhi''s dystopic underbelly, Titli, the youngest member of a violent car-jacking brotherhood plots a desperate bid to escape the ''family'' business.</span>\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OOqiQiMkXDA', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'titli'),
('Guddu Ki Gun', '6', 'Guddu ki Gun is a Adult comedy based movie.<br>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/guudu.jpg', 'Sheershak Anand,Shantanu Ray Chhibbe', 'Raju Sardar,Gajendra-Vikram', 'Shantanu Ray Chhibber', 'Kunal Khemu,Payel Sarkar,Aparna Sharma, Flora Saini, Brijendra Kala,Jameel Khan,Sumeet Vyas', '2015-10-30', 'If you are comfortable watching adult comedies, this one could entertain you because it actually has comedy. For a change, the baton of sex-related humor moves to the gents and hence it is quite a novelty in Bollywood. When it comes to using logic, obviously the film fails. If only, the film had songs which were watchable, it could have been a relief. Guddu Ki Gun is laughable in parts only if you promise to apply no brains all through it. I am going with a 2.5/5 for this adult comedy.&nbsp; ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LAWlBaXSOZY', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'guddu-ki-gun'),
('Hate Story 3', '6', '<div><font face="Tahoma"><span style="font-size: 11px;">What happens when Love turns hate, hate turns betrayal. Hate Story 3 is a venomous thriller set in today''s corporate world, filled with Loathe, Lies &amp; Revenge.The story revolves around Aditya Singh (Sharman Joshi) &amp; Siya Singh (Zareen Khan) who control the family business after the sad demise of Aditya''s elder brother Vikram. Enter their life is an unknown businessman Saurav Singhania (Karan Singh).&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><fo', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/hate_story_3_first_look_4c18cfcc39', 'Vishal Pandya', 'Meet Bros, Amaal Mallik, Baman', 'Bhushan Kumar', 'Sharman Joshi, Zarine Khan, Daisy Shah, Karan Singh Grover, Puja Gupta', '2015-12-04', '\n\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1Y7XhiWUvo', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'hate-story-3'),
('Four Pillars Of Basement', '6', '<span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 11px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Four Pillars Of Basement is a psychological thriller that shows human frailities and capricious nature. The protagonist Samir is a conniving person and works as a security officer in a mall.</span> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Four-Pillars-Of-Basement_2926a115c', 'Giresh Naik K', 'Mudasir Ali, Anurag Mohan', 'Gautam Bafna, Pravin Chudasama', 'Dillzan Wadia, Bruna Abdullah, Aaliya Singh, Zakir Hussain, Shawar Ali, Anant Jog, Shiva Rindan, Ravi Gadariya', '2015-11-06', '\nOnly for the first few scenes of the film, you''ll have the urge to appreciate the novel idea it brings to the table - of twin souls - which isn''t quite the same thing as soulmates. But, soon enough its tacky production, overdramatic sequences and novice actors will distract you.The story keeps harping on how two people complete each other but the lingering unsolicited gyaan is the final blow to your patience. After 107 minutes of incessant rambling about righteousness and morality, the film attempts to end on an inventiv', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XNRvhGMEfY4', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'four-pillars-of-basement');
