('Tamasha', '6', '<span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">In spite of the caption â€˜Why Always The Same Storyâ€™, Imtiaz repeats himself and digs deeper into his style of storytelling. In certain portions, Tamasha is like Jab We Met meets Rockstar and thatâ€™s what disappoints as we the film does not elevate itself from his previous works. Tamasha is certainly a one time watch! It is a typical Imtiaz Ali film .</span>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Tamasha.jpg', 'Imtiaz Ali', 'A R Rahman', 'Sajid Nadiadwala', 'Ranbir Kapoor,Deepika Padukone,Ishtiyaq Khan', '2015-11-27', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Tamasha is the story of a conventional good boy we often refer to as the ''Hero'' in India, played by Ranbir Kapoor &nbsp;who breaks free and leaves for Corsica for a no-frills experience.There he meet a girl of his kind Deepika Padukone (Tara Maheshwari) and the two decide to have fun. But what happens when their lovely unexpected vacation comes to an end,This one is definitely going to make the younger generation itch for a vacation and leave moviegoers teary', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VN_qxutU_qc', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'tamasha'),
('Dilwale', '6', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Meera (Kajol) breaks up with her lover, Raj (Shah Rukh Khan), after she finds out he is a notorious gangster. Years later, when they comes to know of the story, Veer (Varun Dhawan), Raj''s brother, and Ishita (Kriti Shanon), Meera''s sister, decide to unite the lovers in order for their own love story to succeed.</span></font> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Dilwale.jpg', 'Rohit Shetty', 'Pritam Chakraborty', 'Rohit Shetty', 'Shah Rukh Khan,Kajol,Varun Dhawan,Kriti Sanon,Varun Sharma,Chetna Pande,Vinod Khanna,Kabir Bedi,Johnny Lever,Boman Irani,Sanjay Mishra,Mukesh Tiwari,Murli Sharma,Pankaj Tripathi,Nawab Shah,Shawar Ali', '2015-12-18', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">&nbsp;It is a perfect concoction of romance, action and comedy that 6 film viewers generally look forward to. Even though it does not have the engaging storyline of Om Shanti Om, it is just about as, or even more entertaining, than Happy New Year. If entertainment is why you go to the theatres, then Dilwale will not disappoint you. The ending, however, is likely to receive applause only from the die-hard SRK fans. In all, it is a great family film with a comi', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=boj_755o7jk', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'dilwale'),
('Bajirao Mastani', '6', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Bajirao Mastani is based on the life of Peshwa Bajirao and his ladylove Mastani. The filmmaker has planned to make this dream for last 15 years and finally the project has been green-lighted by producers Eros International. Baji Rao was the prime minister to the fourth Maratha Chhatrapati Shahu from 1720. He was credited with expanding the Maratha empire. Ranveer will be seen as Bajirao opposite his lovelady Deepika as Mastani.&nbsp', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Bajirao.jpg', 'Sanjay Leela Bhansali', 'Unknown', 'Kishore Lulla,Sanjay Leela Bhansali', 'Ranveer Singh,Deepika Padukone,Priyanka Chopra,Tanvi Azmi,Vaibbhav Tatwawdi,Mahesh Manjrekar,Milind Soman,Ayush Tandon,Sanjay Mishra', '2015-12-18', '<font color="#555555" face="arial, Helvetica, san-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);">&nbsp;Also the film falls short on several accounts. First of all, it seems confused whether it should be a romance or historic film, swerving between Bajirao wanting to be the famous warrior and the eternal lover. Second, is its pace. The film hardly moves in the first hour or so, picking up speed only after the intermission â€“ in fact it seems a little rushed in the second hal', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NDEExEhvk1Y', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'bajirao-mastani'),
('Wazir', '6', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">''Wazir'' is a tale of two unlikely friends, a wheelchair-bound chess grandmaster and a brave ATS officer, bought together by grief and a strange twist of fate, the two men decide to help each other win the biggest games of their lives. But there''s a mysterious, dangerous opponent lurking in the shadows, who is all set to Checkmate them.</span></font> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/WAZIR_cc93bff48b050ba43e4f73ab23b3', 'Bejoy Nambiar', 'NA', 'Vidhu Vinod Chopra', 'Amitabh Bachchan, Farhan Akhtar, Aditi Rao Hydari,John Abraham,Neil Nitin Mukesh,Manav Kaul', '2016-01-08', '<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: arial, Helvetica, san-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);">Wazir is a smart movie - which could have been way smarter. Wazir is held together by Amitabh Bachchan who shows why he is the Grandmaster of this game. But the tension just isn''t hard enough.But when it over-indulges itself - its writers and editors are the same - the game slips into stalemate. It''s a pity because Wazir''s lead performances, its glassy cinematography, it', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LaEEJEea7-E', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'wazir'),
('Ghayal Once Again', '6', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">It is based on a real-life event in the life of a Mumbai Police encounter specialist.</span></font> ', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Ghayal.jpg', 'Sunny Deol', 'Shankar Mahadevan, Ehsaan Noorani, L', 'Sunny Deol', 'Sunny Deol,Om Puri,Murli Sharma, Prachi Desai,Soha Ali Khan,Tisca Chopra,Shivam Patil,Aanchal Munjal,Rishabh Arora,Daina Khan', '2016-02-05', '<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: arial, Helvetica, san-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);">Whatâ€™s Bad: Ajay Mehra is not as powerful as he was back then. His character lacks the aggression. It seems like the villain is a hero in this film. A tighter script would have worked well. Watch or Not?: If you are a big fan of Ghayal then let me warn you this is no where close to it. Unless you have nothing to do this weekend, watching Ghayal Once Again could be an o', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0UdxNxNArXU', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'ghayal-once-again'),
('Airlift', '6', '<font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">The story of the upcoming movie Airlift is based on a historical human evacuation drama. The film will be set in the time of the 1990 Iraqi invasion of Kuwait that left hundreds of Indians homeless. The film will showcase true events and is set in the 199os, the period of the Gulf War in Kuwait. It will shed light on the civilian evacuation which saw more than 1,70,000 thousand Indians being evacuated from the war hit Kuwait.</span>', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Airlift.jpg', 'Raja Krishna Menon', 'Unknown', 'Aruna Bhatia, Monisha Advani, Madhu Bhojwani, Vikram Malhotra, Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar,Nikhil Advani', 'Akshay Kumar,Nimrat Kaur, Purab Kohli, Kumud Mishra,Prakash Belawadi', '2016-01-22', '<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: arial, Helvetica, san-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);">AIRLIFT is a classic film based on a real life incident that is told extremely well on screen. It is surely one of the best films to come out this year and will pick up with a strong word of mouth. Just do not miss this one!</span>\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LKssCmXa45s', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'airlift'),
('Chauranga', '6', '<div><font face="Arial, Verdana"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Set in the dark hinterland of India where tradition and modernity collide precariously, Chauranga is inspired by a real incident. Fourteen-year-old Santu wants to go to school like his older brother Bajarangi.</span></font></div><div><span style="font-size: 13.3333px; font-family: Arial, Verdana;">When Bajarangi comes home from boarding school on holiday, he exposes Santu to the dreams of city life. But Santu''s destiny was pre-', 'http://moviereport.in/admin/upload/Chauranga_4c63fe9ea843cb056802b9d1', 'Bikas Ranjan Mishra', 'Vivek Philip', 'Sanjay Suri, Onir, Mohan T Mulani', 'Sanjay Suri,Riddhi Sen,Soham Maitra, Tannishtha Chatterjee, Arpita Chatterjee, Ena Saha, Dhritiman Chatterjee, Delzad Hiwale, Anshuman Jha', '2016-01-08', '\n', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nu50meFTNU4', '01/04/16 09:10', '01/04/16 09:10', NULL, 'chauranga'),
